\id JOB - Baibal Kathoung New Testament
\h JOB
\toc1 JOB
\toc2 Job
\toc3 Job
\mt1 JOB
\mt2 (The Book of Job)
\c 1
\s1 Uz ram vah Job hoi a imthung
\p 
\v 1 Uz ram dawk tami buet touh ao teh, a min teh Job doeh. Ahni teh toun hane awm hoeh, tamikalan, Cathut ka taket e, kahawihoehe lamthung ka roun e lah ao.
\v 2 Capa 7 touh hoi canu 3 touh a tawn.
\v 3 A tawn e naw teh, tu 7,000, kalauk 3,000, maitotan 500, lamanu 500, hoi a sannaw moikapap a tawn. Ahni teh Kanîtholae taminaw pueng hlak tami ka lentoe poung e lah ao.
\p 
\v 4 A capanaw ni kum tangkuem amamae a khenae pawi a sak awh navah, amamae im dawk bu canae pawi a sak awh teh a kamkhueng awh navah, a tawncanunaw ka 3, touh hai canei hanelah ouk a coun.
\v 5 Hottelah bu canae pawi abaw hnukkhu vah, Job ni a kaw awh teh, ouk a kamkhueng sak awh. Amom a thaw teh ahnimae milu kuep lah hmaisawi thuengnae sathei ouk a poe. Bangkongtetpawiteh Job ni ka capanaw ni yonnae sak awh vaiteh, a lungthin hoi Cathut hah pahnawt awh langvaih telah ati. Hottelah, Job ni pou a sak.
\s1 Setan ni Job hringnae a taran
\p 
\v 6 Cathut e capanaw BAWIPA e hmalah tâconae hnin a pha torei teh, Setan hai ahnimouh koe a tho van.
\v 7 BAWIPA ni Setan koe nâ lahoi maw na tho atipouh. Setan ni BAWIPA talai van ka kâhei teh ka kumluennae koehoi, atipouh.
\p 
\v 8 BAWIPA ni Setan koe ka san Job he na pouk boimaw. Talai van dawk ahni patetlae toun han kaawm hoeh e, tamikalan Cathut ka taket e hoi, kahawihoehe lamthung ka roun e awm hoeh, telah atipouh.
\p 
\v 9 Setan ni BAWIPA a pathungnae teh, Job ni Cathut hah a khuekhaw awm laipalah maw a taki.
\v 10 Ahni teh a imthung hoi, a tawn e naw pueng hoi, a tengpam pueng pet na kalup teh, a kut hoi a tawk e naw pueng hah yawhawi na poe teh, na kamphung sak nahoehmaw.
\v 11 Atuvah na kut pho nateh a tawn e hnonaw pueng hah tek pouh haw, na hmaitung roeroe vah nama tang na pahnawt han doeh atipouh.
\v 12 BAWIPA ni, Setan koe, khenhaw! a tawn e naw pueng teh, nange na kut dawk ao. Ama teh tek hanh atipouh. Hahoi Setan teh BAWIPA koehoi a tâco.
\p 
\v 13 Hnin touh hnin teh, a canu hoi a capanaw teh, a hmau kacue im dawkvah a ca awh teh misurtui a nei awh lahun nah,
\v 14 Job koe patoune buet touh a yawng teh, maitotannaw talai a kanawk awh lahun nah, lanaw hai ateng a pâ awh lahun navah,
\v 15 Sheba taminaw ni na tuk awh teh, koung a la awh toe na sannaw hah tahloi hoi a thei awh teh, kai buet touh dueng doeh, nang koe dei hanelah ka hlout atipouh.
\v 16 A dei lahun nah tami alouke bout a tho. Kalvan hoi Cathut e hmai a bo teh, tu hoi na sannaw hah koung a kak teh be a kahma toe. Kai buet touh dueng doeh nang koe dei hanelah ka hlout e lah ka o atipouh.
\p 
\v 17 A dei lahun nah tami alouke bout a tho. Khaldean taminaw ahu kathum touh lah ao awh teh, kalauknaw hah koung na lawp awh, na sannaw hai tahloi hoi be a thei awh. Kai buet touh dueng doeh nang koe dei hanelah ka hlout atipouh.
\p 
\v 18 A dei lahun nah tami alouke bout a tho. Na canu hoi na capanaw ni, a hmau kacuepoung e im vah a ca awh teh misurtui a nei awh lahun navah,
\v 19 Khenhaw! kahrawng lahoi kahlî katang poung e a tho teh, imnaw hah a hmang teh, thoundoun, tanglanaw hah koung a ratet teh koung a due. Kai buet touh dueng doeh nang koe dei hanelah ka hlout atipouh.
\p 
\v 20 Hahoi Job ni a thaw teh, ahni a ravei, a lû luengpalueng lah a ngaw teh, talai dawk a tabo teh a bawk.
\v 21 Anu e von thung hoi tak caici lah ka tâco teh, tak caici lah bout ka ban han. BAWIPA ni na poe teh BAWIPA ni bout a la. BAWIPA min teh pholennae awm seh telah a ti.
\v 22 Hetnaw dawkvah Job ni yonnae sak laipalah Cathut yonpennae tawn hoeh.
\c 2
\s1 Setan ni Job tanouknae
\p 
\v 1 Cathut e capanaw BAWIPA e hmalah a tâconae hnin bout a pha toteh, Setan hai BAWIPA e hmalah kamnue van hanlah ahnimouh koe a tho van.
\v 2 BAWIPA ni Setan teh nâ lahoi maw na tho atipouh. Setan ni BAWIPA a pathungnae teh, talai van ka kâhei teh, ka kumluennae koehoi, atipouh.
\p 
\v 3 BAWIPA ni Setan koevah, ka san Job heh na pouk boimaw. Ahni patetlae toun han kaawm hoeh e, tamikalan, Cathut ka taket e hoi, kahawihoehe lamthung ka roun e, apihai awm hoeh. Bang hoeh e dawk na ka raphoe nakunghai ama min la doeh poe awm ti atipouh.
\p 
\v 4 Setan ni BAWIPA hah a pathung teh, vuen hanlah vuen lah doeh ao, tami ni a tawnta e pueng hah a hring nahanelah a kâpasoung yawkaw han.
\v 5 Hateiteh, atu na kut pho nateh, a hru hoi atak tek pouh haw, na hmaitung vah na pahnawt han doeh atipouh.
\p 
\v 6 BAWIPA ni Setan koe, khenhaw! ahni teh na kut dawk ao. Hateiteh a hringnae hah pâhlung atipouh.
\v 7 Setan teh BAWIPA e hmaitung hoi a tâco teh, Job hah a khok koehoi a lû totouh, ka patawpoung e moihna hoi a kawi sak.
\v 8 A kâkoe nahanelah Job ni ampaikei hah a la teh hraba dawk a tahung.
\p 
\v 9 A yu ni, na lannae hah pou na kuet han rah maw. Na Cathut hah thoebo nateh, dout lawih atipouh.
\v 10 Hateiteh ahni ni napui koe, ka pathu e napui ni lawk a dei e patetlah na dei. Bangtelamaw Cathut koehoi hawinae ka hmu katang teh, thoenae hai hmawt mahoeh maw, telah atipouh. Hete hno pueng dawk Job ni apâhni dawk hoi yonnae dei hoeh.
\s1 Job hoi a huinaw kathum
\p 
\v 11 Job e a hui kathum touh ni, het patet e hawihoehnae ni a pha sin e a thai awh torei teh, amamouh aonae koehoi lengkaleng a tho awh. Teman tami Eliphaz Shuhi tami Bildad hoi, Naamath tami Zophar, bangkongtetpawiteh, ahni lungpahawi hane, lungmawng sak hanelah a kamkhueng awh teh a kâpan awh.
\v 12 Ahnimouh ni ahlanae koehoi Job hah a khet awh navah, nout thai awh hoeh. Kacaipounglah a ka awh teh, khohnanaw hah vekvek a ravei awh teh, a lûnaw dawk vaiphu a kâphuen awh.
\v 13 Hottelah hnin sari touh hoi rum sari touh thung talai dawk a tahungkhai awh teh, apinihai ahni koe lawk kam touh hai dei awh hoeh. Bangkongtetpawiteh, a lungmathoe poung tie hah a panue awh.
\c 3
\s1 Job ni a khenae hnin thoe a bo
\q1 
\v 1 Hathnukkhu, Job ni a pahni dawk hoi a khenae hnin hah thoe a bo.
\q1 
\v 2 Job ni ati e teh,
\q1 
\v 3 ka khenae hnin hah kahmat pawiteh,
\q2 capa a vawn ati e tangmin hai kahmat pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 4 Hatnae hnin hah hmonae lah awm pawiteh,
\q2 Cathut ni lathueng lahoi khen hanh naseh.
\q2 Hoehpawiteh, angnae ang hanh naseh.
\q1 
\v 5 Hmonae hoi duenae tâhlip ni ramuk naseh,
\q2 tâmai ni ramuk e, kanîthun e hmonae ni pakhi naseh.
\q1 
\v 6 Hatnae tangmin hah hmonae ni kuen naseh,
\q2 hatnae kum dawk e hninnaw dawkvah lunghawi van hanh naseh.
\q2 Thapa touknae dawk hai bawk hanh naseh.
\q1 
\v 7 Oe, hatnae tangmin hah kingkadi e tangmin lah awm pawiteh,
\q2 lunghawinae kamthang pai hanh naseh.
\q1 
\v 8 Tuitam thaw sak hane coungkacoe kaawmnaw ni, hatnae hnin hah,
\q2 thoekâbonaw ni thoebo awh naseh.
\q1 
\v 9 Hatnae tangmin amom lae âsi hah mawm naseh,
\q2 angnae hah tawng awh naseh. Hateiteh, hmawt awh hanh naseh.
\q2 Kanî a tâco e hai, hmawt hanh naseh.
\q1 
\v 10 Bangkongtetpawiteh, anu e thun hah khan hoeh eiteh,
\q2 ka mithmu vah, ka lungmathoenae hah kâhrawk hoeh.
\q1 
\v 11 Bangkongmaw ka tâco tahma vah, ka due hoeh va.
\q2 Bangkongmaw von dawk hoi ka tâco nah, kahmakata hoeh va.
\q1 
\v 12 Bangkongmaw phai dawk tawm e lah ka o,
\q2 bangkongmaw ka nei hane sanutui na pânei.
\q1 
\v 13 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka i vaiteh, karoumcalah ka o han ei,
\q2 mat ka i vaiteh, ka kâhat hane boum.
\q1 
\v 14 Talai siangpahrang hoi khokhangkungnaw,
\q2 ka rawk e bout ka kangdout sakkungnaw hoi vah,
\q1 
\v 15 hoehpawiteh, sui ka tawn e tami ka lentoe e,
\q2 a im dawk ngun hoi kakawi sak naw hoi vah,
\q1 
\v 16 hoehpawiteh, thakoup hoehnahlan ka khe e camo,
\q2 angnae kahmawt boihoeh e, camo patetlah, kapawk e lah ka o hoeh va.
\q1 
\v 17 Hawvah tamikathoutnaw ni, runae a sak e hah a kâhat awh teh,
\q2 hawvah thakatawnnaw hah a kâhat awh.
\q1 
\v 18 Hawvah thongkabawt e cungtalah a kâhat awh teh,
\q2 repcoungroe pawlawk hai thai hoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 19 Hawvah tami kathoung kalen naw cungtalah ao awh teh,
\q2 a sannaw hah a bawi koehoi a hlout.
\q1 
\v 20 Bangkongmaw runae ka khang e koevah, angnae poe e lah ao teh,
\q2 bangdawkmaw a lung ka mathout e koe hringnae hah poe e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 21 Due han a ngai poung, hateiteh, tho hoeh.
\q2 Pakawp e râw hlak vah, hoe ka pataw e ka tawng e,
\q1 
\v 22 phuen a hmu awh navah,
\q2 dei thai hoeh e a lung kahawi katang e koevah,
\q1 
\v 23 bangdawkmaw a lamthung hro lah kaawm e koevah,
\q2 angnae hah poe e lah ao. Cathut ni rapan hoi kalupsin e koevah,
\q1 
\v 24 Bangkongtetpawiteh, rawca yueng lah ka cingou teh
\q2 ka khuikanae mitphi hai tui ka lawng e palang patetlah doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 25 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka takipoung e hah,
\q2 ka tak dawk a pha teh, ka ngaihri poung e ni na thosin.
\q1 
\v 26 Ka phunep hoeh dawk duem kaawm thai hoeh.
\q2 Kâhat panuek hoeh, bangkongtetpawiteh, rucatnae ni a pha telah ati.
\c 4
\s1 Eliphaz ni lawk a dei
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi Teman tami Eliphaz ni ahni koe bout a dei e teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 nang koe lawk kam touh ka dei haw vai, na thaima han vaimoe.
\q2 Hatei apinimaw dei laipalah ao thai han.
\q1 
\v 3 Tami moikapap na cangkhai toe.
\q2 Kut tha kaawm hoeh e tha na o sak.
\q1 
\v 4 Na lawk ni karawmnaw hah a thaw sak teh,
\q2 khokpakhu tha kaawm hoeh e tha ao sak.
\q1 
\v 5 Hateiteh, atu nama koe a pha teh,
\q2 na lung sut a pout.
\q2 Na tek teh, na ngaihmang.
\q1 
\v 6 Na barilawa e hoi na kâuepkhai e nahoehmaw,
\q2 kakuep e lamthung hah na ngaihawi e nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 7 Atu pouk haw, kayonhoehe apimaw kahmakata boi vai.
\q2 Hat hoehpawiteh, tamikalan hah nâmaw tâkhawng e lah ao boi.
\q1 
\v 8 Kahmanae dawkvah payonpakainae,
\q2 talai kanawk teh runae ka tu e ni doeh ouk a a.
\q1 
\v 9 Cathut e kâha dawk a kahma awh teh,
\q2 a lungkhueknae kâha dawk be a kak awh.
\q1 
\v 10 Sendek huk e pawlawk hoi,
\q2 ka matheng poung e sendektan kanaw e a hâ hah a kâkhoe.
\q1 
\v 11 Ca hane ao hoeh dawkvah Sendek matawngnaw a kamlum teh,
\q2 Sendek manu e a canaw teh koung kâkapek awh.
\q1 
\v 12 Atu arulahoi kai koe lawk a pha teh,
\q2 ka hnâ ni arulahoi pouk e hah a thai.
\q1 
\v 13 Karoumcalah a i awh lahun navah,
\q2 karum vah vision hah pouk lahun navah,
\q1 
\v 14 Takinae hoi pâyawnae kai koe a pha.
\q2 Ka hrunaw pueng koung kâhlehlawk sak e han,
\q1 
\v 15 Hottelah muitha teh,
\q2 ka hmalah a kâhlai teh,
\q2 ka muen rueng a thaw.
\q1 
\v 16 Hote muitha hah a kangdue teh, ka kamnuek e hah kapek thai hoeh.
\q2 Ka mithmu vah hno buet touh a kamnue, duem ao teh lawk hah ka thai.
\q1 
\v 17 Ka dout thai e tami heh, Cathut hlak vah a lan thai maw,
\q2 tami heh kasakkung hlak vah a thoung thai na maw.
\q1 
\v 18 A sannaw patenghai kâuepkhai hoeh niteh, kalvantaminaw hai na payon tet pouh pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 19 amhru im dawk kho ka sak niteh, a kungpui teh,
\q2 vaiphu lah ao teh, ahnimanaw teh, khakbara ni patenghai a tâ thai e hah
\q2 bangtelamaw hoe a yuem thai han.
\q1 
\v 20 Amon hoi tangmin totouh katipcalah a kâbawng teh,
\q2 apinihai tek laipalah a yungyoe a kahma awh.
\q1 
\v 21 Ahawi poungnae naw hai koung takhoe lah ao teh,
\q2 lungangnae awm laipalah be a due awh telah atipouh.
\c 5
\q1 
\v 1 Atu kaw haw, na ka pato hane ao awh han vaimoe.
\q2 Kathounge tami, nâ lah maw na kamlang han.
\q1 
\v 2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lungkhueknae ni tamipathu a thei teh,
\q2 utsinnae ni kamawngrame a thei.
\q1 
\v 3 Tami ni khawngyang a pabo e hah ka hmu,
\q2 hateiteh kho a saknae hmuen hah thoe tangka bo.
\q1 
\v 4 A capanaw teh, a hlout nahane awm hoeh,
\q2 longkha koe a rawp awh vaiteh, a katin awh han.
\q2 Ka rungngang hane awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 5 Bangkongtetpawiteh, a von ka hlam e ni a a e cang hah be a ca pouh teh,
\q2 pâkhingum e patenghai hnopainaw hah a lawp awh.
\q1 
\v 6 Bangkongtetpawiteh, khangnae teh talai dawk hoi ka tho e nahoeh.
\q2 Rucatnae hai talai dawk hoi ka tho e na hoeh.
\q1 
\v 7 Hmaitali kahlun lah a luen e patetlah,
\q2 tami teh rucat hane doeh a khe.
\q1 
\v 8 Hateiteh, kai niteh, Cathut ka tawng vaiteh,
\q2 ka rucatnae teh Cathut e hmalah ka dei pouh han.
\q1 
\v 9 A bawilennae hoi dei thai hoeh e, touk thai hoeh e,
\q2 kângairunae kasakthaie koe vah.
\q1 
\v 10 Talai dawk kho a rak sak teh,
\q2 law dawk tui a lawng sak.
\q1 
\v 11 Kangduenae hmuen ka rahnoum e hah, a rasang sak teh,
\q2 lung kamathoutnaw hah, roumnae hmuen dawk a luen sak.
\q1 
\v 12 Huenghai kaawmnaw khokhangnae hah a kahma sak teh,
\q2 a kut hoi a noe e naw koung a raphoe pouh.
\q1 
\v 13 Tami lungkaang huenghai kaawm e hah,
\q2 a thoumthainae ni a man awh teh, huenghai kaawm naw e khokhangnae hah,
\q2 amamouh dawk tang a pha han.
\q1 
\v 14 Kanîthun angnae dawk hmonae hoi a kâhmo awh teh,
\q2 kanî tuengtalueng thun nah tangmin e patetlah thupthup a payam awh.
\q1 
\v 15 Hateiteh, tahloi hoi tami ka voutthoup e hah a rungngang teh,
\q2 athakaawme taminaw e apâhni hoi a kut ni a rungngang awh.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka roedengnaw ni ngaihawinae a tawn awh teh,
\q2 lanhoehnae ni a pahni a cakuep pouh.
\q1 
\v 17 Khenhaw! Cathut ni a toun e tami teh, tami a lung kahawi e doeh.
\q2 Hatdawkvah Athakasaipounge ni phepnae teh, noutna laipalah awm hanh.
\q1 
\v 18 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ama ni a hem teh, a hmâ hah ama ni a kawm pouh.
\q2 Ama ni a hmâ a ca sak teh, a kut hoi a dam sak.
\q1 
\v 19 Ama ni runae taruk touh dawk hoi a tâco sak e dueng khout laipalah,
\q2 sari touh thung dawk hoi hai kahawihoehe ni tek awh mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 20 Ama ni takang duenae thung hoi a ratang awh vaiteh,
\q2 taran um e tahloi thaonae thung hoi a ratang awh han.
\q1 
\v 21 Lawkthoeumkha thung hoi hro lah na o vaiteh,
\q2 rawkphainae a pha torei teh, na taket mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 22 Rawkphainae hoi takangnae na panui sin vaiteh,
\q2 talai e sarangnaw hah na taket mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 23 Bangkongtetpawiteh, kahrawng e talungnaw hoi rei kambawng vaiteh,
\q2 kahrawng e sarangmathengnaw hoi karoumcalah na o awh han.
\q1 
\v 24 Na onae rim dawk karoumcalah na o e hah na panue han.
\q2 Na khosaknae hah na khet navah voutthoupnae banghai awm mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 25 Na ca catoun moiapap hane hah a panue vaiteh,
\q2 nange na miphunnaw talai dawk phovai patetlah ao e hah na hmu han.
\q1 
\v 26 Atueng pha toteh cabong taoung e patetlah na kumcue toteh,
\q2 phuen koe na pha han.
\q1 
\v 27 Khenhaw! heteheh ka pakhingpalang awh teh, kalan e doeh ka tho.
\q2 Thaihaw, nama hane doeh tie hah panuek, telah atipouh.
\c 6
\s1 Job ni Eliphaz a pathung
\q1 
\v 1 Job ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Oe, ka kângairunae heh, yawcu dawk khing haw pawiteh,
\q2 ka khang e runae naw hai, yawcu khingnae dawk phat naseh.
\q1 
\v 3 Bangkongtetpawiteh, palang teng e sadi hlak hai a ri han doeh.
\q2 Hatdawkvah ka dei payon toe.
\q1 
\v 4 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Athakasaipounge ni a ka e pala teh kai thung vah ao,
\q2 ahnimae a sue hah ka muitha ni a nei.
\q2 Cathut takinae hah ka hmalah a kamnue.
\q1 
\v 5 Kahrawng e la ni hram a papnae koe a hram boimaw,
\q1 
\v 6 Atuinae kaawm hoeh e bu teh palawi laipalah ca thai han maw.
\q2 Aduirakei ka pangaw e dawk atuinae bangmaw kaawm.
\q1 
\v 7 Ka hringnae ni, a tek han a ngai hoeh e,
\q2 kai hanelah, panuettho e rawcanaw doeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Oe, kahei e heh ka hmawt haw pawiteh,
\q2 Cathut ni ngai poung e na poe haw pawiteh.
\q1 
\v 9 Pahren lahoi Cathut ni vek na khei haw na seh,
\q2 A kut na pho sin nateh vitkatip lah, na tâtueng haw naseh,
\q1 
\v 10 Hottelah nakunghai, ka lungmawngnae ka tawn rah.
\q2 Patawnae ni na tha hoeh nakunghai ka lunghawi han rah.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tami kathounge lawk hah kâhrawk mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 11 Bangpatete thaonae maw ka tawn teh, ka ngaihawi han rah.
\q2 Ka poutnae hah, banglamaw ao teh, ka hringnae ni a saw sak han rae te,
\q1 
\v 12 Ka thaonae heh lungsong thaonae lah maw ao.
\q2 Ka takthai he rahum lah maw a tho.
\q1 
\v 13 Ka thung vah kabawmkung awmhoeh namaw,
\q2 ka kuepcingnae naw pueng kai koehoi be kampuen toung nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 14 Bangpueng katetthai takinae a ceitakhai nakunghai,
\q2 patawnae ka khang e koevah, a hui koehoi a lungmanae kamnue sak hane doeh.
\q1 
\v 15 Ka hmaunawnghanaw teh palang tui patetlah yuengyoe kampuen e doeh,
\q2 dawngdengca dawk kahmat e palang tui patetlah ao awh.
\q1 
\v 16 Tui a kamkak e kecu dawkvah a tamang teh,
\q2 a thungvah ka kâhrawk e tadamtui patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 17 Abet torei teh, be kahma awh teh,
\q2 a kâan torei teh amamae hmuen koehoi kahmakata awh.
\q1 
\v 18 Amamae a lamthung dawk hoi a kamlang awh teh,
\q2 nâ lahai cet laipalah kahmakata awh.
\q1 
\v 19 Teman miphun kahlawng kacetnaw ni a khet awh teh,
\q2 Sheba kahlawng kacetnaw ni a ngaihawi awh.
\q1 
\v 20 A ngâhawi awh dawkvah, a lungpout awh.
\q2 Hawvah a pha awh torei teh, a kaya awh.
\q1 
\v 21 Bangkongtetpawiteh, atuvah banglahai na tho awh hoeh toe.
\q2 Takikatho e na hmu awh teh, na lung a puen awh.
\q1 
\v 22 Na poe awh haw, telah ka dei boimaw, hoeh pawiteh,
\q2 na hnopainaw dawk hoi, kai na ratang nahanelah poe awh ka ti boimaw,
\q1 
\v 23 Hoeh pawiteh, ka tarannaw e kut dawk hoi na rungngang awh haw, ka ti boimaw,
\q2 hoeh pawiteh, kai ka hnephnap e koehoi na ratang awh ka ti boimaw.
\q1 
\v 24 Na cangkhai awh haw, duem ka o han,
\q2 lawkkalan hah na panuek sak awh.
\q1 
\v 25 Lannae teh, banghloimaw a tha ao.
\q2 Hateiteh, na lawknaw ni bangmaw a kamceng sak.
\q1 
\v 26 Lawk ka dei e naw heh yonpen hane maw na ngai awh.
\q2 Ngaihawinae ka tawn hoeh e tami ni a dei e lawk teh, kahlî patetlah doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 27 Nangmouh niteh, naranaw hah na ka pacekpahlek awh,
\q2 na huinaw hanelah tangkom na tai pouh awh.
\q1 
\v 28 Hatdawkvah, pahren lahoi khen awh haw,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, nangmae hmalah ka lai kathout mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 29 Ban awh nateh, lanhoehnae hah awm sak awh hanh,
\q2 atu totouh ka kangdout e ka lannae heh tawm awh.
\q1 
\v 30 Ka lai dawk lanhoehnae ao maw,
\q2 katui hoi katui hoeh e na kapekkaboe thai awh hoeh maw.
\c 7
\q1 
\v 1 Talaivan dawkvah tami hanelah thaw ka ru e thaw a onae tueng ouk ao nahoehmaw,
\q2 a hninnaw hai kutkapânaw e hnin patetlah awm hoeh namaw.
\q1 
\v 2 Tâhlip dik ka doun e san patetlah,
\q2 kutkapânaw ni kutphu hmu han a ngai hawi e patetlah.
\q1 
\v 3 Bang hoeh e dawk thapa moikapap lah ka hno teh,
\q2 khohmo runae naw hah kai hanelah ao toe.
\q1 
\v 4 Ka i na koehoi, nâtuek maw ka thaw han.
\q2 Karum heh baw nah lawiseh ka ti.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, khodai totouh kamhmei kamlang hoi ka o.
\q1 
\v 5 Ka takthai teh, pâri hoi songnawng ni muen na kayo teh,
\q2 ka vuen hai cupei teh koung a kâhnoum.
\q1 
\v 6 Ka hninnaw teh, hnikawngnae yawngyen hlak hai a rang teh,
\q2 ngaihawinae awm laipalah a loum.
\q1 
\v 7 Ka hringnae teh kahlî doeh tie hah pahnim hanh,
\q2 ka mit ni ahawinae bout hmawt mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 8 Na kahmawtnaw e mit ni bout na hmawt mahoeh toe.
\q2 Na mit ka tak dawk a um navah, kaawm mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 9 Tâmai kâhin teh, a kahma e patetlah,
\q2 duenae tangkom thung ka cet e ni bout ban mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 10 A im vah bout ban hoeh vaiteh,
\q2 a onae hmuen ni ama teh panuek mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 11 Hatdawkvah ka pahni ka cakuep mahoeh.
\q2 Ka muitha rek na laihoi ka dei vaiteh,
\q2 kakhat e ka hringnae hoi lai ka roe han.
\q1 
\v 12 Kai teh, talî lah maw ka tho.
\q2 Nahoeh pawiteh, talî dawk e khorui lah maw ka tho teh,
\q2 na karingkung hah na ta pouh.
\q1 
\v 13 Ka ikhun ni ka ngai a mawng sak han.
\q2 Ka yannae ikhun ni ka phuenangnae a roum sak han telah ka ti navah,
\q1 
\v 14 Tangmin mang lahoi na pakhi teh,
\q2 kamnuenae lahoi kai na kalue sak.
\q1 
\v 15 Ka hringnae ni ka lahuen a kara hoi duenae hah,
\q2 ka takthai ni a ngaihnawn.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka hringnae he ka hnueai teh, yungyoe ka hring mahoeh.
\q2 Kama dueng na awm sak awh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka hringnae teh a kahû lah doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 17 Tami he banglamaw ao teh, hettelah na tawmrasang teh,
\q2 a lathueng vah na lungthin pou na ta.
\q1 
\v 18 Amon tangkuem na tho sin teh,
\q2 nâtuek e atueng dawk hai pou na tanouk.
\q1 
\v 19 Nâtuek hai na kamlang takhai laipalah, pou na khet vaiteh,
\q2 ka tamtui ka padoun nahai ka madueng na tat hoeh.
\q1 
\v 20 Yonnae ka tawn maw,
\q2 oe taminaw ka ring e,
\q2 nang lathueng vah bangmaw ka sak.
\q2 Bangdawkmaw na hmaitung vah telah na o sak teh,
\q2 kama hoi kama hnori lah na o sak.
\q1 
\v 21 Bangdawkmaw na kâ ka eknae hah na ngaithoum laipalah,
\q2 ka payonpakainae hah na lat pouh hoeh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, vaiphu dawk ka i vaiteh,
\q2 nama ni kai na tawng han, hatei kaawm mahoeh toe atipouh.
\c 8
\s1 Bildad ni lawk a dei
\p 
\v 1 Shuhi tami Bildad ni a pathung teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Nâsittouh maw he e hnonaw heh dei han,
\q2 na pahni dawk hoi ka tâcawt e lawk hah athakaawme kahlî patetlah ao han.
\q1 
\v 3 Cathut ni kalan hoeh lah lawk a ceng boimaw,
\q2 nahoeh pawiteh, Athakasaipounge ni, lannae a kamlang takhai boimaw.
\q1 
\v 4 Na capanaw ni ama taranlahoi yon awh pawiteh,
\q2 kâtapoenae kecu dawk a tâkhawng han.
\q1 
\v 5 Cathut hah atangcalah hoi, na tawng teh,
\q2 Athakasaipounge koevah, kâheinae na sak pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 6 Tamikathoung tamikalan lah na awm pawiteh,
\q2 nang hanelah atu roeroe thaw vaiteh,
\q2 lanae hmuen koe hawinae na coe sak han.
\q1 
\v 7 Na kamtawngnae a thoung nakunghai,
\q2 na poutnae a len katang han.
\q1 
\v 8 Bangkongtetpawiteh, pahrennae hoi a yan e hnonaw hah pakhingpalang haw,
\q2 na mintoenaw ni a hmu e hnonaw hah pouk haw.
\q1 
\v 9 Bangkongtetpawiteh, paduem e tami la o awh teh,
\q2 banghai panuek awh hoeh. Bangdawk tetpawiteh, talai van e hnin tha naw teh,
\q2 tâhlip patetlah doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 10 Ahnimae lungthin thung hoi ka tâcawt e lawknaw ni, na dei pouh awh teh,
\q2 na cangkhai hoeh namaw.
\q1 
\v 11 Tuinawk laipalah lungpum a roung thai han namaw.
\q2 Tui laipalah capi teh a roung thai han namaw.
\q1 
\v 12 A hring nah tâtueng hoeh nakunghai,
\q2 alouke akungnaw hlak palang a kamyai.
\q1 
\v 13 Cathut kapahnimnaw e a lamthung teh, hot patetlah ao.
\q2 Tami kahawihoehnaw e ngaihawinae teh a kahma han.
\q1 
\v 14 A kâuepkhai awh e teh, tâkhawng pouh lah ao han,
\q2 a kâuepkhainae teh, Bombarui patetlah doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 15 A im dawk a kamngawi ei kangdout thai hoeh.
\q2 Kacakcalah a kuet ei pou cak thai ma hoeh.
\q1 
\v 16 Khobetnae koe dikkahringcala a roung teh,
\q2 a kangnaw ni takha koung tahloi awh.
\q1 
\v 17 A tangpha ni talung khakdeng teh,
\q2 talung um vah a tangpha a payang nahane a tawng.
\q1 
\v 18 Amae hmuen koehoi phawk lah ao torei teh,
\q2 pou kacak mahoeh, telah a kâpahnawt han.
\q1 
\v 19 Khenhaw! het hateh, lunghawinae lamthung lah a o,
\q2 talai dawk hoi aloukenaw hah a pâw han.
\q1 
\v 20 Khenhaw! Cathut ni toun han kaawm hoeh e na tâkhawng hoeh vaiteh,
\q2 thoe ka sak e teh kangdout sak mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 21 Na kâko teh panuinae hoi akawi sak vaiteh,
\q2 na pahni hai lunghawinae lawk hoi akawi sak han.
\q1 
\v 22 Nang kahmuhmanaw hah yeiraipo sak vaiteh,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw e rim teh awm mahoeh toe telah a ti.
\c 9
\s1 Job ni Bildad a pathung
\p 
\v 1 Job ni bout a pathung teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Hetheh doeh tie hah atangcalah ka panue,
\q2 hateiteh, Cathut e hmalah bangtelamaw tami teh a lan thai han.
\q1 
\v 3 Ama oun han ka ngai e awm pawiteh,
\q2 avai 1,000 touh dawkvah vai touh boehai pathung thai mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 4 Cathut teh, lungkaang poung e, athakaawme thayung lah ao.
\q2 Ama taranlahoi lung ka patak sak e,
\q2 a lam ka cawn e apimaw kaawm boi.
\q1 
\v 5 Monnaw hah a puen teh, a lungkhueknae hoi
\q2 a pathung torei teh, panuek awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 6 Talai a onae hmuen koehoi a kâhuet teh,
\q2 a khomnaw hah koung a kâhuet sak.
\q1 
\v 7 Kanî hah kâ a poe teh, tâcawt hoeh.
\q2 Âsi angnae hah muen a ramuk.
\q1 
\v 8 Ama dueng lahoi kalvan hah a ramuk teh, tuipui tuicapa van a cei.
\q1 
\v 9 Ama ni Latum, Kangduetaphai, Baritca,
\q2 hoi akalae âsinaw hah a sak.
\q1 
\v 10 Be panue thai hoeh e hnokalen e hai,
\q2 touk thai hoeh e kângairu hnonaw hah a sak.
\q1 
\v 11 Ka teng vah a cei ei ama teh, ka hmawt hoeh.
\q2 Na ceihlawi e hai ka panuek hoeh.
\q1 
\v 12 Ama ni lat pawiteh, apinimaw a haw pouh thai han.
\q2 Apinimaw bangmaw na sak, atipouh thai han.
\q1 
\v 13 A lungkhueknae dawk hoi, Cathut ni kamlang takhai mahoeh toe.
\q2 A khok rahim vah tami kâoup e kabawmnaw teh a tabut awh.
\q1 
\v 14 Kai ni ama teh bangtelamaw, ka pathung thai han.
\q2 Ama oun nahanelah, bangpatet e lawk maw kârawi han
\q1 
\v 15 Bangtelah kalan nakunghai, ama teh ka pathung thai mahoeh.
\q2 Kai lawkcengkung koe pahrennae doeh ka hei hnawn han.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka kaw pawiteh, ama ni na pato han.
\q2 Ama ni ka lawk na thai pouh hane ka yuem hoeh.
\q1 
\v 17 Bangkongtetpawiteh, kahlî kathout ni na hmang teh,
\q2 a khuekhaw awm laipalah ka hmânaw hah a kampai sak.
\q1 
\v 18 Ka kâha thai laipalah, reithai hoi na kawi sak.
\q1 
\v 19 A thasainae dawkvah ama teh, athakaawme lah ao.
\q2 A lannae, kong dawk tetpawiteh,
\q2 lawkcengnae dawk apinimaw ka hnin hah a khoe thai han.
\q1 
\v 20 Ka kuep nakunghai, ka pahni ni yon na pen han,
\q2 tanouk hanelah kaawm hoeh nakunghai, ka lanhoehnae hah a kamnue sak han.
\q1 
\v 21 Toun hoeh nahanlah ka o.
\q2 Hateiteh, ka kâpanuek hoeh, ka hringnae heh ka hnueai toe.
\q1 
\v 22 Be kâvan doeh.
\q2 Hat dawk nahoehmaw, tamikathoutnaw hoi toun han kaawm hoeh e hoi,
\q2 be raphoe han telah ka dei vaw.
\q1 
\v 23 Hemnae ni vai touh hoi thet boipawiteh,
\q2 kayonhoehe khangnae teh, a panuikhai han.
\q1 
\v 24 Talai heh tamikathout e kut dawk poe lah ao teh,
\q2 a lawkcengkungnaw e minhmai a ramuk.
\q2 Ahni hoehpawiteh, api han na maw.
\q1 
\v 25 Ka hninnaw hateh, ka yawng e hlak hai hoe a rang,
\q2 a kamleng awh teh, hawinae hmawt awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 26 Karang poung e lawng patetlah a khup teh,
\q2 Mataw ni moithang a ka cawp e patetlah a rang.
\q1 
\v 27 Ka phuenangnae ka pahnim vaiteh,
\q2 ka lungmathoenae minhmai he ka ta vaiteh,
\q2 minhmai kapancala ka o han ka ti navah,
\q1 
\v 28 Ka khangnae naw pueng heh, makkhak ka taki teh,
\q2 tamikayon hoeh e lah na pouk hoeh langvaih tie hah ka panue.
\q1 
\v 29 Yon pen e lah kaawm pawiteh,
\q2 bangdawkmaw ahrawnghrang e meng ka tawk han.
\q1 
\v 30 Tadamtui hoi ka kamhluk nakunghai,
\q2 ka kut heh sapet hoi ka kamsin nakunghai,
\q1 
\v 31 tangdong dawk na tâkhawng teh,
\q2 ka khohna ni patenghai na panuet han doeh.
\q1 
\v 32 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lawkcengnae koe rei cet vaiteh,
\q2 ama teh ka pathung thai nahanelah, ama teh tami lah tho hoeh.
\q1 
\v 33 Maimouh roi e van kut ka toung hanelah,
\q2 maimae rahak laicei awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 34 Kai koe e sonron lat naseh
\q2 taki a thonae ni na taket sak hanh seh.
\q1 
\v 35 Hatdawkvah ama taket laipalah lawk hah ka dei han.
\q2 Hateiteh, kai koevah hottelah bout awm kalawn hoeh.
\c 10
\q1 
\v 1 Kamae ka hringnae ka panuet.
\q2 Ka phuenangnae ka pâpho ngala han.
\q2 Ka hringnae a rek hoi lawk ka dei han.
\q1 
\v 2 Cathut koe yon na pen hanh, bangdawkmaw na taran,
\q2 na hmawt sak haw, telah ka ti han.
\q1 
\v 3 Tami repcoungroe lahoi na kutsak tami hah dudam teh,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw khokhang e hnâbokhaie heh, ahawi telah na pouk maw.
\q1 
\v 4 Takthai e mit maw na tawn,
\q2 tami ni a hmu e patetlah maw na hmu van maw.
\q1 
\v 5 Namae hninnaw hai tami e hnin patetlah maw ao.
\q2 Namae kumnaw teh, tami e hnin patetlah maw ao.
\q1 
\v 6 tamikathout lah ka ohoehnae hah na panue eiteh,
\q2 na kut dawk hoi ka rungngang thai e awm hoeh tie hah na panue nahlangva,
\q1 
\v 7 Ka payonpakai e naw hah na tawng teh,
\q2 ka yonnae hah na pâphue.
\q1 
\v 8 Namae na kut hoi na sak teh,
\q2 ka kuepcingcalah na pathoup.
\q2 Hateiteh, namae kut ni bout na raphoe.
\q1 
\v 9 Nama ni talai e na sak tie hah na pahnim hoeh nahan ka kâhei,
\q2 vaiphu lah maw bout na coung sak han.
\q1 
\v 10 Nama ni sanutui patetlah na rabawk teh,
\q2 sanutui kamkak patetlah na pahlawm nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 11 Nama ni ka vuen hoi takthai na ramuk.
\q2 Ka hru hoi ka tharui hoi na caksak nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 12 Nama ni ka hringnae hoi pahrennae na poe teh,
\q2 na khetyawtnae ni ka muitha teh a lungmawng sak.
\q1 
\v 13 Hete hnonaw heh na lungthin thung vah na hro teh,
\q2 namae thung vah ao tie hah ka panue.
\q1 
\v 14 Ka yon pawiteh nama ni na panue han.
\q2 Ka payonpakai e dawk hoi na hlout sak hoeh.
\q1 
\v 15 Tamikathout lah kaawm pawiteh, yawthoe lah ka o han,
\q2 tamikalan lah ka o nakunghai, minhmai kahawi kahmawt thai mahoeh.
\q2 Kayayeirai hoi runae hoi kakawi e la ka o.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka kâoup pawiteh, ka matheng e Sendek patetlah,
\q2 hmâ na ca sak. Kai taranlahoi takikathopounge bout na kamnue sak.
\q1 
\v 17 Kai na ka taran hane ka panuekkhaie patuen patuen na tha teh,
\q2 kai dawk na lungkuephoehnae na pung sak.
\q2 Dumyennae hoi tarantuknae hah, kai koe pou ao.
\q1 
\v 18 Bangdawkmaw camo im dawk hoi na tâcosak.
\q2 Oe apinihai na hmawt laipalah kadout boi pawiteh;
\q1 
\v 19 Kaawmhoehe patetlah ka o han ei,
\q2 Camo im thung hoi phuen lah ceikhai lah ka o han ei.
\q1 
\v 20 Ka hninnaw heh, ka younca e nahoehmaw.
\q2 Ka cei vaiteh bout ka ban thai hoeh nahanlah,
\q2 duenae tâhlip hoi hmonae ram dawk ka cei hoehnahlan vah.
\q1 
\v 21 Lungmawngnae dawngdeng hai ka hmu nahanelah,
\q2 ka kâhat pawiteh, ka mahmawk na awm sak awh.
\q1 
\v 22 Ama lungpouk ka hmawt e, kingkahmawt e ram,
\q2 duenae tâhlip patetlah, banghai ka awmhoeh e,
\q2 angnae hai hmonae patetlah a onae hmuen koe, telah ati.
\c 11
\s1 Zophar ni lawk a dei
\p 
\v 1 Naamath tami Zophar ni a pathung e teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Hettelae lawk kapap e heh pathung laipalah ao thai han namaw,
\q2 Lawk moikapap ka dei e pueng ni maw kayonhoehe la o awh han.
\q1 
\v 3 Na dei e lawk hrawnghrang ni, tami a roum sak thai han namaw,
\q2 Tami na panuikhai nah buet touh ni hai yue mahoeh namaw.
\q1 
\v 4 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka yuemnae teh a thoung.
\q2 Na mithmu vah kathoung telah na ti.
\q1 
\v 5 Hateiteh, oe Cathut ni na dei pouh seh,
\q2 nang kâtaran lahoi pahni ang naseh.
\q1 
\v 6 Ama ni lungangnae arulawk hah na hmu sak yawkaw han,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, na lungangnae alet hni touh apap.
\q2 Hatdawkvah na payonpakai e dawk hoi kayounhnawn lah Cathut ni a sak tie panuek.
\q1 
\v 7 Kadungpoung e Cathut e hno hah na pakhingpalang thai na maw,
\q2 Athakasaipounge coungnae hah
\q2 na tawng teh koung na hmuthai maw.
\q1 
\v 8 Kalvan hlak hai a rasang teh, nang ni bangmaw na sak thai,
\q2 Phuennaw hlak hai hoe adung teh, nang ni bangmaw na panue.
\q1 
\v 9 A bangnuenae teh, talai hlak hai asaw.
\q2 Tuipui hlak hai hoe akaw.
\q1 
\v 10 A man teh thongim dawk paung hoi lawkceng hanelah pâkhueng pawiteh,
\q2 apinimaw ahni teh a rungngang thai han.
\q1 
\v 11 Bangkongtetpawiteh, huenghai ao a e hah a panue,
\q2 thoe sak e hai a hmu.
\q2 Ama ni pouk laipalah maw ao han.
\q1 
\v 12 Bangkongtetpawiteh, kahrawng e laca patetlah tami a khe torei teh,
\q2 tamipathu teh a lungang han.
\q1 
\v 13 Na lungthin hah kârakueng nateh
\q2 Cathut koe na kut dâw haw.
\q1 
\v 14 Na kut dawk na payonpakai e awm boipawiteh, ahlanae koe tâkhawng haw.
\q2 Kathoute hah na im dawk awm hanh seh.
\q1 
\v 15 Hottelah tounnae awm laipalah, na minhmai hah a kamnue han doeh.
\q2 Kacakcalah na o vaiteh, na taket mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 16 Bangkongtetpawiteh, na rucatnae hah na pahnim vaiteh,
\q2 poun ka lawng e tui patetlah pahnim hanh.
\q1 
\v 17 Na hringnae teh kanîthun e hlak hai hoe a ang han,
\q2 a hmonae hah amom patetlah ao han.
\q1 
\v 18 Karoumcalah na o han,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, ngaihawinae ao.
\q2 Na tengpam e hno na sung nakunghai karoumcalah na kâhat han.
\q1 
\v 19 Na i vaiteh, apinihai tâsuenae na poe mahoeh,
\q2 tami moikapap ni nang koe a kâhei awh han.
\q1 
\v 20 Hateiteh, tamikathoutnaw e mit teh, dawn vaiteh,
\q2 hlout awh mahoeh.
\q2 A ngaihawi awh e hringnae teh a sung awh han telah a ti.
\c 12
\s1 Job ni Zophar a pathung
\p 
\v 1 Job ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Lunghringnae awm laipalah
\q2 nangmanaw nahoehmaw tami lungkaangnaw lah na kaawm awh heh,
\q2 namamouh hoi lungangnae teh rei a due han.
\q1 
\v 3 Hateiteh, nangmouh patetlah panuethainae ka tawn van.
\q2 Nangmouh hlak vah hoe ka rahnoum hoeh.
\q2 Het patet e hno panue hoeh e apimaw kaawm.
\q1 
\v 4 Kai teh, huikonaw ni panuikhaie lah ka o teh,
\q2 Cathut a kaw teh, ama ni a pathung e kai heh,
\q2 tamikalan, toun han awmhoeh,
\q2 a panuikhaie kâhmo e lah ka o.
\q1 
\v 5 Kanawmcalah kaawmnaw e khopouknae dawkvah,
\q2 yawthoenae heh panuikhainae lah ao teh,
\q2 a kamthui nahanlah coungkacoe paloung pouh e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 6 Dingcanaw e rim law teh a hmacawn teh,
\q2 Cathut lungkhueksakkungnaw law teh a roum awh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh Cathut ni a kut hoi a kawkhik.
\q1 
\v 7 Hateiteh, atu moithangnaw koe pacei nateh, na cangkhai awh han doeh.
\q2 Kalvan e kamleng e tavanaw hai pacei haw, na dei pouh han doeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Hoeh pawiteh, talai koe vah dei pouh haw, na cangkhai han doeh,
\q2 Talî dawk e tanganaw ni nangmouh teh
\q2 kamcengcalah na panue sak han doeh.
\q1 
\v 9 Hete hnonaw dawk BAWIPA ni a sak tie hah,
\q2 ka panuek hoeh e nangmouh thung dawk apimaw kaawm.
\q1 
\v 10 A kut dawk hringnae katawnnaw puenghoi,
\q2 tami pueng e kâhanae ao.
\q1 
\v 11 Kâko ni rawca a patek e patetlah
\q2 hnâ ni lawk hah a tanouk nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 12 Kacuenaw koe lungangnae ao teh,
\q2 a kumcue torei teh, panuethainae ao.
\q1 
\v 13 Ahni koe lungangnae hoi thaonae ao.
\q2 Ahni ni khokhangnae hoi panuethainae a tawn.
\q1 
\v 14 Hno heh raphoe hnukkhu hoi teh, bout sak thai hoeh toe,
\q2 tami khak paung hoi teh tâco thai nahan a ru toe.
\q1 
\v 15 Tui hah pahak hoi teh a ke toe,
\q2 tui bout tha torei teh talai dawk bout a kamuem.
\q1 
\v 16 Ama koe thasainae hoi roumnae a onae hoi
\q2 ka payonsakkung teh amae doeh.
\q1 
\v 17 Khokhangkungnaw hah be kahma lah a ceikhai teh,
\q2 lawkcengkung hah be a pathu sak.
\q1 
\v 18 Siangpahrangnaw kateknae hah a rathap pouh teh,
\q2 a kengnaw dawk taisawm a kâyeng sak awh.
\q1 
\v 19 Bawinaw hah takcaici lah a hrawi teh,
\q2 athakaawme taminaw hah a rawp sak.
\q1 
\v 20 A kâuepkhai awh e lawknaw hah a hnoun pouh teh,
\q2 kacuenaw e panuethainae hah a takhoe pouh awh.
\q1 
\v 21 Bawinaw lathueng vah dudamnae a rabawk teh,
\q2 tami tha kaawm naw hah kutcaici lah ao sak.
\q1 
\v 22 Hmonae thung hoi kadung poung e hno koung a kamnue sak,
\q2 Duenae tâhlip hah angnae dawk a tâcokhai,
\q1 
\v 23 Miphunnaw hah a len sak teh bout a raphoe.
\q2 Miphunnaw hah a kâthap sak teh bout a hrawi.
\q1 
\v 24 Talai e tamihu kahrawinaw hah panuethainae naw a kahma sak teh,
\q2 kahrawngum lamthung a ohoehnae koe a kâva sak.
\q1 
\v 25 Angnae awm laipalah hmonae thung thupthup a payam awh,
\q2 ka parui e tami patetlah rawraw a cu sak.
\c 13
\q1 
\v 1 Khenhaw! he e hnonaw pueng heh, ka mit hoi ka hmu.
\q2 Ka hnâ ni a thai teh a thaipanuek.
\q1 
\v 2 Nangmouh ni na panue e teh, kai ni hai ka panue van.
\q2 Nangmouh hlak hoe ka rahnoum hoeh.
\q1 
\v 3 Hateiteh, Athakasaipounge koevah, ka dei haw nei,
\q2 Cathut hoi rei pouk hanelah ka ngai poung.
\q1 
\v 4 Hateiteh, nangmouh teh
\q2 laithoe ka dei e lah na o awh.
\q1 
\v 5 Duem awm awh haw, hottelah pawiteh,
\q2 na lungangnae la ao han ei.
\q1 
\v 6 Ka pouknae heh thai awh haw,
\q2 ka pahni dawk hoi ka tâcawt e kâheinae heh alawkpui lah pouk awh.
\q1 
\v 7 Cathut hanelah kahawihoeh poung lah a dei awh han maw,
\q2 Ahni hanelah laithoe na dei awh han maw.
\q1 
\v 8 Ahni hanelah kapeknae na tawn awh na maw,
\q2 Cathut teh na oun awh han maw
\q1 
\v 9 Ama ni nangmanaw hah rek na toun awh pawiteh, ahawi han namaw.
\q2 Tami a panuikhaie patetlah ama hah na panuikhai han namaw.
\q1 
\v 10 Arulahoi kapeknae na tawn awh pawiteh,
\q2 ama ni na yue awh roeroe han doeh.
\q1 
\v 11 Ahawinae ni na lungpuen sak awh mahoeh maw.
\q2 Taki thonae hah nangmouh dawkvah bawt mahoeh maw
\q1 
\v 12 Namamae cingthuinae lawk hah,
\q2 hraba cingthuinae lawk doeh.
\q2 Na kângainae khorapan hai tangpung hoi pacawp rumram e la doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 13 Duem awm awh haw, lawk na dei sak haw.
\q2 Ka tak dawk banghai phat na yawkaw seh.
\q1 
\v 14 Bangdawkmaw ka tak hah ka hâ hoi ka kei vaiteh,
\q2 ka hringnae hah ka kut dawk ka ta han.
\q1 
\v 15 Na ka thet nakunghai ama teh kâuepkhai han doeh.
\q2 Hottelah nakunghai a hmalah yonthanae lawk bout ka dei han.
\q1 
\v 16 Ama teh kaie rungngangnae lah ao han.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tamitongthoenaw teh a hmalah tho thai mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 17 Ka dei e heh kahawicalah thai awh haw,
\q2 ka pâpho e heh na hnâ dawk kâen sak.
\q1 
\v 18 Khenhaw! ka dei e kong dawkvah yo ka pouk e doeh toe,
\q2 yon na ngaithoum han tie hah ka panue.
\q1 
\v 19 Apimaw na ka oun hane kaawm.
\q2 Awm boipawiteh, duem ka o vaiteh, ka due yawkaw han.
\q1 
\v 20 Kai dawk hno kahni touh dueng heh sak hanh yawkaw,
\q2 hottelah pawiteh nang koehoi kâhrawk mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 21 Kai koehoi na kut hah ahla poungnae koe kampuen sak,
\q2 taki na thonae e ni ka lungpuen sak hanh naseh.
\q1 
\v 22 Hottelah pawiteh na kaw nah na pathung han.
\q2 Hoeh pawiteh lawk na dei sak haw, nama ni na pathung.
\q1 
\v 23 Ka payonpakai e hoi ka yonnae hah nâyittouh maw apap vai,
\q2 kâtapoenae hoi ka yonnae hah na panuek sak haw.
\q1 
\v 24 Bangdawkmaw na minhmai na hro teh, na taran lah na pouk.
\q1 
\v 25 Kahlî ni a palek e lengle teh, na pâlei han na maw,
\q2 Cakong hah na pâlei han namaw
\q1 
\v 26 Bangkongtetpawiteh, kakhat e hno hah,
\q2 kai na taranlahoi na thut teh,
\q2 ka nawca nah payonpakai e naw hah na phu sak.
\q1 
\v 27 Ka khok hlong na buet teh,
\q2 ka lamthung pueng hah kahnaicalah na khet.
\q2 Ka khoksampha hanelah rui khoup na payang.
\q1 
\v 28 Tami teh kahmawn e hno patetlah atum teh,
\q2 khakbara ni a ca e hnicu patetlah doeh ao.
\c 14
\q1 
\v 1 Napui ni a khe e tami teh,
\q2 a hring kaduem ni teh runae hoi kakawi e doeh.
\q1 
\v 2 A pei patetlah a kamdat teh bout a kamyai.
\q2 Tâhlip patetlah a kampuen teh, bout awm hoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 3 Hot patetlae dawkvah, na mit na padai teh,
\q2 lawkcengnae dawk nama koe na ceikhai han na maw.
\q1 
\v 4 Apinimaw kathounghoehe dawk hoi,
\q2 na thoung e a la thai han,
\q2 apinihai lat thai mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 5 A hninnaw hah atueng khoe hnukkhu hoi,
\q2 thapa nâyittouh maw tie hah na kut dawk ao.
\q2 A tapuet thai hoeh nahanelah khori hoi a ngang pouh.
\q1 
\v 6 Kut ka pâ e tami patetlah a hninnaw aloum totouh,
\q2 a kâhat thai nahanelah ahni teh kamlang takhai haw.
\q1 
\v 7 Bangkongtetpawiteh, thing teh tâtueng nakunghai
\q2 bout a bawt hane letlang hngaihawinae ao rah.
\q2 A cakang bout a bawt han.
\q1 
\v 8 Talai dawk a khawngyang kahmawn nakunghai
\q2 kadout nakunghai.
\q1 
\v 9 Tui kahû dawk bout bawt vaiteh,
\q2 ung e patetlah a cakang a tâco han doeh.
\q1 
\v 10 Hateiteh, tami teh a due hoi pakawp teh a kahma toe,
\q2 tami teh a kâha a baw teh namaw ao.
\q1 
\v 11 Talî dawk e tui a kahma teh,
\q2 tuipui hai a hak teh be a ke.
\q1 
\v 12 Hot patetlah tami hai a yan teh thaw hoeh toe.
\q2 Kalvannaw ao hoeh totouh hai kâhlaw hoe toe.
\q2 Hoeh pawiteh, muet a inae koehoi kâhlaw mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 13 Oe phuen koe na hrawk sak haw,
\q2 na lungkhueknae a roum hoeh roukrak
\q2 na hrawk haw, atueng hah na pouk pouh nateh,
\q2 na pahnim hanh.
\q1 
\v 14 Ka kâthungnae atueng a pha totouh,
\q2 tami dout pawiteh, bout a hring han namaw
\q2 Ka ru e ka thawnaw dawk hoi ka ring han.
\q1 
\v 15 Na kaw vaiteh, na pato han.
\q2 Nama ni na kut hoi na sak e teh na pahren han.
\q1 
\v 16 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka khokhnuknaw pueng be na touk.
\q2 Hateiteh, ka yonnae naw hah na khen pouh hanh.
\q1 
\v 17 Kâtapoenae hah, yawngya thung khakkin e naw lah ao teh,
\q2 ka payonpakai e hah na ramuk.
\q1 
\v 18 Hateiteh, mon katim e patetlah,
\q2 talung teh a onae hmuen koehoi puen e patetlah,
\q1 
\v 19 tui ni talung pekpacin e patetlah,
\q2 tuikalen ni talai kahawi a ceikhai e patetlah,
\q2 tami e ngaihawi e hah na raphoe.
\q1 
\v 20 Ama teh poe na tâ teh, be a kahma awh.
\q2 A mei na kâthungsak teh, alouklah na cei sak.
\q1 
\v 21 A capanaw a tawmrasang e hah panuek awh hoeh.
\q2 Ahnimouh pabo lah o awh e hai kâhmawt thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 22 Hateiteh, a takthai hah patawnae dawk ao vaiteh,
\q2 a hringnae ni ama a khui han telah a ti.
\c 15
\s1 Eliphaz ni Job yon a pen
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi Teman tami Eliphaz ni a pathung.
\v 2 Hat navah,
\q1 Tami a lungkaang ni ahrawnghrang panuenae hoi maw a pathung han.
\q2 Kanîtholae kahlî hoi a von a paha sak han namaw.
\q1 
\v 3 Bang patopatang kaawm hoeh e lawk hno lahoi thoseh,
\q2 hawinae ka sak thai hoeh e lawk ni a poukkhai han maw.
\q1 
\v 4 Cathut takinae hoi ama koe ratoum e hah na ngang pouh.
\q1 
\v 5 Bangkongtetpawiteh, na payonpakainae ni,
\q2 na pahni hah a cangkhai teh, huenghai onae lawk hah na kârawi.
\q1 
\v 6 Kai ni nang yon na pen hoeh.
\q2 Na pahni roeroe ni doeh yon na pen.
\q1 
\v 7 Hmaloe poung khe e lah maw na o,
\q2 hoeh pawiteh monnaw ao hoehnahlan vah sak e lah na o toung maw.
\q1 
\v 8 Cathut e khokhangnae hah na panue toung maw,
\q2 Lungangnae he nang hane dueng lah maw ao.
\q1 
\v 9 Kaimouh ni ka panue hoeh e bangmaw na panue,
\q2 kaimouh dawk kaawm hoeh e bangmaw na panue thai.
\q1 
\v 10 Kaimouh thung dawkvah sampo ka po e hoi kacuepoung e,
\q2 na pa hlak hai kacuehnawn e ka o awh kaima.
\q1 
\v 11 Cathut ni a dei e lungmawngnae lawk kanem teh
\q2 nang hanlah a patawpoung maw
\q1 
\v 12 Bang kecu dawk maw, na lungthin ni na kahmakhai,
\q2 bang kecu dawk maw avangvanglah pou na hmaiet.
\q1 
\v 13 Na muitha ni Cathut taranlahoi pou a kamlang teh,
\q2 hot patet e lawknaw na pahni dawk hoi na tâco sak.
\q1 
\v 14 Tami teh banglamaw ao teh, a thoung thai han.
\q2 Napui ni a khe e teh, banglamaw ao teh, a lan thai han.
\q1 
\v 15 A tamikathoungnaw patenghai,
\q2 Cathut ni kâuepkhai hoeh.
\q2 A mithmu vah kalvan patenghai thounghoeh pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 16 Panuet ka tho e, kakhin e, payonpakainae hah,
\q2 tui patetlah ka net e teh, banghloimaw hoe kathounghoehe la ao han.
\q1 
\v 17 Thaihaw, ka dei vai,
\q2 ka hmu e hah ka pâpho han.
\q1 
\v 18 Tami a lungkaangnaw ni ouk a dei e
\q2 mintoe koehoi e hmu e hno a hro awh hoeh e hah.
\q1 
\v 19 Ahnimouh dueng a poe e ram,
\q2 ram alouknaw a othaihoenae hah.
\q1 
\v 20 Tamikathoutnaw ni a hring na thung patawnae a khang.
\q2 Amamouh kum yit touh rep kacuengroenaw koe a hro.
\q1 
\v 21 Takitho e pawlawk hah amamae hnâ ni a thai teh,
\q2 hnopai a tawn nah, ka raphoe hane naw ni a thosin awh.
\q1 
\v 22 Hmonae thung hoi kamlang hane hah yuem hoeh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ahni teh tahloi ni a ring toe.
\q1 
\v 23 Ca hane tawng hanelah a kâva teh,
\q2 nâmaw hote teh ao telah a ti.
\q2 Hmonae hnin teh a kut dawk a pha toe tie hah a panue.
\q1 
\v 24 Rucatnae hoi kângairunae ni a lungpuen sak,
\q2 tarantuk hanelah coungkacoe kaawm e siangpahrang patetlah tâ e la ao.
\q1 
\v 25 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut taranlahoi a kut a dâw teh,
\q2 Athakasaipounge taranlahoi kâoupnae hoi a kâroe.
\q1 
\v 26 Bahling katha poung e hoi, lung ka patak poung e lahoi
\q2 Cathut tuk hanelah a yawng sin.
\q1 
\v 27 Athaw ni a minhmai muen a ramuk teh,
\q2 a keng thouk kathâw nakunghai,
\q1 
\v 28 kingkadi e khopui dawk kho a sak teh,
\q2 apinihai a ohoehnae, kingdi e kho dawk ao.
\q1 
\v 29 Tawnta mahoeh, hoeh pawiteh, a tawnta e hnopainaw kangning mahoeh,
\q2 hoeh pawiteh a tawn e hah talai dawk pungdaw mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 30 Hmonae thung hoi tâcawt mahoeh.
\q2 Hmaipalai ni a kangnaw hah a kak han,
\q2 a pahni dawk e kahlî hoi be a kahma sak han.
\q1 
\v 31 Amahoima a kâdum teh, bang hoeh e hah kâuep han seh,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, a tawkphu teh banghai bang nahoeh.
\q1 
\v 32 Atueng akuep hoehnahlan vah, kuep sak lah ao awh vaiteh,
\q2 akangnaw hah naw mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 33 Misurkangnaw patetlah ka hmin hoeh rae a paw a sarut totouh kahû en vai teh,
\q2 Olive thing patetlah a pei hah koung a sarut han.
\q1 
\v 34 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tamikathoutnaw hoi kamyawng e teh,
\q2 caici lah ao han. Tadawngnae hoi sak e im teh, hmai ni be a kak han.
\q1 
\v 35 Kahawi hoeh e hah a vawn teh, bang hoeh e hah a khe awh.
\q2 A von dawk laithoe a vawn awh telah a ti.
\c 16
\s1 Job ni Eliphaz a pathung
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi Job ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Hot patet e hno teh, moikapap ka thai toe,
\q2 nangmouh abuemlae lungpahawinae haiyah thathoenae hrum doeh.
\q1 
\v 3 Kahlî lawk teh poutnae ao maw,
\q2 Hettelah pathung hane bang ni maw na tha a hmei sak.
\q1 
\v 4 Ka kangduenae hmuen heh na kangduenae hmuen lah awm pawiteh,
\q2 kai ni hai na dei awh e hah ka dei thai van han.
\q1 
\v 5 Hateiteh, ka pahni ni tha na o sak awh han.
\q2 Ka pahni dawk hoi lungroumnae lawk ni na lungmathoenae a kahma sak han.
\q1 
\v 6 Lawk ka dei nakunghai ka lungmathoenae roum sak thai hoeh.
\q2 Duem ka o nakunghai bang alânae awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 7 Hateiteh, ama ni na tawn sak teh,
\q2 ka huikonaw puenghai kingdi sak toe.
\q1 
\v 8 Nama ni khakkatek teh,
\q2 hot ni kai hanelah kapanuekkhaikung lah ao.
\q2 Ka kamsoenae ni yon na pen teh, hot ni ka minhmai dawk ka panuek khai e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 9 A lungkhueknae ni rekrek na sei teh, na hmuhma.
\q2 A hâkam na kata sin teh, ka taran ni na hmaiet.
\q1 
\v 10 Pahni na ang sin awh teh,
\q2 lungroukatetlah ka tangboung dawk na tambei.
\q2 Kai na taran hanelah cungtalah a kamkhueng awh.
\q1 
\v 11 Cathut ni Cathut banglah ka ngaihoeh naw koe na pâseng,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw kut dawk na tâkhawng.
\q1 
\v 12 Kanawmcalah ka o eiteh, ama ni rekrek na bawng.
\q2 Ka lahuen dawk na man teh, bengbeng na kahuet teh,
\q2 rek ka kâbawng, kai teh tâkhawng hanelah ka o.
\q1 
\v 13 Ahnie pala kakanaw ni na kalup awh.
\q2 Ka lung poukkayawng lah na ka teh,
\q2 na pahren hoeh, talai dawk ka hmu e tui hah a ka rabawk.
\q1 
\v 14 Ka hmâ dawkvah patuen patuen hmâ na paca
\q2 ka pahngawpahrak e ransanaw patetlah na cusin.
\q1 
\v 15 Ka vuen dawkvah, burihni ka khui sin teh,
\q2 ka lû teh vaiphu dawk ka hruek.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka ka lawi vah ka minhmai a paling teh,
\q2 ka mit dawk duenae tâhlip ao.
\q1 
\v 17 Ka kut dawk kahawihoehe hno kasake awm hoeh.
\q2 Ka ratoumnae teh a thoung ei te.
\q1 
\v 18 Oe talai, ka thipaling heh ramuk han haw.
\q2 Ka kanae ni kâhatnae hmuen tawn hanh naseh.
\q1 
\v 19 Atu patenghai, kapanuekkhaikung teh
\q2 a rasangnae koevah ao.
\q1 
\v 20 Ka huinaw ni na dudam awh.
\q2 Cathut koe ka mitphi a lawng.
\q1 
\v 21 Tami ni imri hanelah, a kâhei pouh e patetlah,
\q2 oe Cathut koe na kâhet pouh hane awm haw pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 22 Bangkongtetpawiteh, kum nâsittouh abaw hoehnahlan,
\q2 bout ban hoeh nae lamthung dawk ka cei han telah ati.
\c 17
\q1 
\v 1 Ka hringnae hah a kâbawng teh, ka hninnaw hai aloum toe.
\q2 Kai hanelah phuen hai coungkacoe lah ao toe.
\q1 
\v 2 Ka panuikhai e hah kai koe awm awh hoeh maw.
\q2 Ka lung ka khuek sak e lawk ka mit a um nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 3 Nama dueng lahoi kai hanelah, lawkkamnae hah sak,
\q2 kut na ka man e teh api han namaw.
\q1 
\v 4 Bangkongtetpawiteh, panuethainae dawk hoi, a lungthin hah na hro.
\q2 Hatdawkvah ahnimouh teh, na rasangsak mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 5 A huiko koe dumnae hoi oupnae lawk ka dei e teh,
\q2 a canaw e mit totouh a mawm han.
\q1 
\v 6 Hateiteh, tamimaya koe kâpankhai rumram hanelah na sak teh,
\q2 ahnimae hmalah tamtui pathasin rumram hanelah ka o.
\q1 
\v 7 Ka lungmathoenae kecu dawk ka mit totouh a mawm teh,
\q2 ka takthai pueng heh tâhlip rumram la ao.
\q1 
\v 8 Tamikalannaw ni hetheh kângairu ati awh han,
\q2 kayonhoehe taminaw ni cathutlaipa e taminaw a taran awh han.
\q1 
\v 9 Hateiteh, tamikalan ni a lamthung hah a kuet vaiteh,
\q2 ka thoung e kut ka tawn e teh hoe a thao han.
\q1 
\v 10 Hateiteh, abuemlahoi pahren lahoi bout ban awh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, nangmouh thung dawkvah
\q2 tamilungkaang ka hmawt pawm mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 11 Ka hninnaw hai aloum toe.
\q2 Ka lungthung hoi ka pouk teh, ka noe e naw hai ayawmyin lah doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 12 Tangmin hah kanîthun lah a kâthungsak teh,
\q2 khohmo thung hai angnae a hnai toe ati awh.
\q1 
\v 13 Phuen hah ka im patetlah ka ring teh,
\q2 hmonae thung vah ikhun ka sak pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 14 rawkphainae hah apa doeh ka ti teh,
\q2 tangraet koe nang teh anu hoi ka tawncanu doeh ka tetpawiteh,
\q1 
\v 15 ka ngaihawinae teh, nâ lah maw ao vai,
\q2 ka ngaihawinae teh, apinimaw a hmu.
\q1 
\v 16 Duenae kho takhang koe lah, a kamleng awh vaiteh,
\q2 vaiphu dawk rei ka kâhat han namaw, telah ati.
\c 18
\s1 Bildad lawk: tami kathoutnaw teh ouk rektap awh
\p 
\v 1 Shuhi tami Bildad ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Nâsittouh maw pout laipalah, lawk heh na tawng han,
\q2 thaipanueknae tawn awh, hahoi lawk na dei pouh han.
\q1 
\v 3 Bang kecu dawk maw moithang patetlah touksin lah o awh teh,
\q2 nangmae mithmu vah tamipathu patetlah ka kâpouk.
\q1 
\v 4 Lungkhueknae hoi namahoima na kâraphoe.
\q2 Nang hanelah talai heh ceitakhai lah ao han maw,
\q2 Hoeh pawiteh, lungsong heh aonae koehoi puen lah ao han maw.
\q1 
\v 5 Tamikathoutnaw e angnae teh roup padue pouh lah ao teh,
\q2 a hmaiang hai ang hoeh.
\q1 
\v 6 Rim e angnae hah a hmo teh,
\q2 ateng e hmaiim teh padue e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 7 A khoksampha a thaonae hah duem sak la ao teh,
\q2 amae khokhangnae ni a tâkhawng han.
\q1 
\v 8 A khok ni tamlawk dawk a kâman sak teh,
\q2 karap thung vah a cei sak.
\q1 
\v 9 A khoksampha dawk tamlawk a man teh,
\q2 ama hah karap dawk a bo.
\q1 
\v 10 Ama hanelah karap hah talai dawk hro e la ao teh,
\q2 lamthung dawk ama hane karap a patung.
\q1 
\v 11 Avoivang hoi takikatho e ni a pakhi teh,
\q2 a hnuk lahoi a pâlei.
\q1 
\v 12 A thaonae hah a thayoun toung dawkvah,
\q2 atengpam vah rawkphainae coungkacoe lah ao.
\q1 
\v 13 Hote runae ni a vuen hah a ca pouh teh,
\q2 duenae camin ni a kutkhok hah a ca pouh.
\q1 
\v 14 A kângue e rim hoi ahni teh takhoe lah ao teh,
\q2 takikatho pounge siangpahrang hmalah tâcokhai e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 15 A tami hoeh e hah rim dawk kho a sak awh teh,
\q2 kho a saknae dawk gan a phuen pouh awh.
\q1 
\v 16 A rahim e a tangpha hah koung a ke teh,
\q2 a lathueng lae akangnaw teh a kamyai.
\q1 
\v 17 Ama pahnim thai hoeh nahanlah talai dawk hoi a kahma teh,
\q2 a min kamthangnaw e um vah a min awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 18 Ahni teh angnae koehoi hmonae dawkvah a hrek teh,
\q2 talai dawk hoi pâlei e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 19 A taminaw thung dawk hoi a capa hoi a na mincanaw tawn hoeh.
\q2 Hoeh pawiteh, a khosaknae dawkvah a imthung buet touh hai cawi mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 20 Ahnie tueng nah kaawm e taminaw ni a taki awh e patetlah,
\q2 ahni hnukkhu kaawm e naw ni hai ahni kecu a kângai a ru awh han.
\q1 
\v 21 Tamikathoutnaw khosaknae koe teh, hot patetlah ao han.
\q2 Hetheteh Cathut ka panuek hoeh naw a onae hmuen doeh telah a ti.
\c 19
\s1 Job ni Bildad a pathung
\p 
\v 1 Job ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Atueng nâsittouh maw ka hringnae he runae na poe awh teh,
\q2 lawk hoi kai na raphoe awh han.
\q1 
\v 3 Vai hra totouh na pathoe awh e ka tak dawkvah
\q2 na payon awh nakunghai na kayak awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 4 Ka payon katang pawiteh,
\q2 ka payonnae teh kai dawk pou ao han.
\q1 
\v 5 Kai na taranlahoi na kâoup awh teh,
\q2 kai kayanae heh kai na tarannae lah na hno awh pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 6 kai dawkvah Cathut a payon tie hoi,
\q2 a tamlawk hoi na ramuk tie hah panuek awh.
\q1 
\v 7 Payonnae kong dawkvah ka hram pawiteh, na thai pouh mahoeh.
\q2 Puenghoi ka hram nakunghai lannae hah awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Ka tapuet thai hoeh nahanlah ama ni ka lamthung hah a pâbing.
\q2 Ka lamthung dawk hmonae hah a ta.
\q1 
\v 9 Ka bawilennae hah na rading pouh teh,
\q2 ka lû dawk e bawilukhung hah na la pouh.
\q1 
\v 10 Avoivang hoi vekvek na phi te ka kahma toe.
\q2 Ka ngaihawinae teh, thingkung patetlah na phawk pouh.
\q1 
\v 11 Kai na taranlahoi a lungkhueknae hah a kâan sak teh,
\q2 a taran buet touh e patetlah na touksin.
\q1 
\v 12 A ransahu hah a kamkhueng awh teh,
\q2 kai na taran lahoi lamthung a rasoun awh,
\q2 ka lukkareirim tengpam petkâkalup lah na ven awh.
\q1 
\v 13 Ka hmaunawnghanaw hah ahla nah koelah na puen pouh teh,
\q2 ka panue e naw hah tamitavan lah koung ao awh.
\q1 
\v 14 Ka imthungnaw hai ka hmawt thai hoeh toe.
\q2 Ka huikahawinaw ni koung na pahnim awh toe.
\q1 
\v 15 Ka im dawk kho kasaknaw,
\q2 ka sannunaw ni imyin lah na pouk awh. Ahnimae mithmu vah imyin lah ka o.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka sannaw hah ka kaw eiteh, na pato awh hoeh toe.
\q2 Lawkkanem hoi pasawt a ngai toe.
\q1 
\v 17 Ka hringnae teh ka yu hanelah a hnueai e lah ao teh,
\q2 rei ka tâcawt e hmaunawnghanaw hanelah ngai ka tho e la awm hoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 18 Camoca ni patenghai na dudam awh.
\q2 Ka thaw navah kai taranlahoi lawk a dei awh.
\q1 
\v 19 Ka huiko kamyawng pueng ni na panuet awh.
\q2 Ka lungpataw e naw ni hai kai tarankung lah koung ao awh.
\q1 
\v 20 Ka vuen hoi ka tak hai ka hru dawk rapkâbet.
\q2 Kahâhli duengdoeh kaawm toe.
\q1 
\v 21 Oe, nangmouh ka huinaw, na pahren awh haw, na pahren awh haw,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh Cathut e kut hoi na hem e la ka o toe.
\q1 
\v 22 Bang kecu dawk maw Cathut na rektap e patetlah kai hah na rektap awh.
\q2 Ka takthai dawk ka khangnae he na khout sak awh hoeh rah maw.
\q1 
\v 23 Oe, ka lawknaw he ca lah ka thun pawiteh,
\q2 cauknaw dawk pakhum boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 24 thutnae sum hoi, talung dawk thut e
\q2 a yungyoe hanelah awm pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 25 kai na karatangkung teh a hring tie hah ka panue.
\q2 A hnuktengpoung nah talai van bout a kangdue han.
\q1 
\v 26 Ka vuen heh raphoe hnukkhu hoi,
\q2 ka takthai hoi Cathut hah ka hmu han tie hah ka panue.
\q1 
\v 27 Kai kama roeroe ni ka hmu vaiteh, ayâ alouk ni a hmu dueng laipalah,
\q2 kai ni kamae mit hoi roeroe ka hmu han.
\q2 Banghloimaw ka thung e ka lungthin ni a rabui.
\q1 
\v 28 Hno coungnae a kung teh, kai dawkvah hmu awh eiteh,
\q2 bangtelamaw, ahni teh rektap han, na tet awh boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 29 Namamouh ni tahloi teh taket awh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lungkhueknae ni tahloi hoi reknae hah tâco sak.
\q2 Lawkcengnae ao tie hah panuethai nahan telah ati.
\c 20
\s1 Zophar lawk
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi Naamath tami Zophar ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Hatdawkvah ka pouk lawi, pathung nahane na poe,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, ka thung e lungreithai kecu dawk doeh.
\q1 
\v 3 Tounnae ni na yue e hah ka thai toe.
\q2 Ka muitha ni thaipanueknae hoi pathungnae na sak pouh.
\q1 
\v 4 Ayan hoi talaivan
\q2 tami ao totouh hoi,
\q1 
\v 5 tamikathoutnaw tânae tueng teh a duem.
\q2 Cathut bang lah kangaihoehnaw e lunghawinae teh,
\q2 dawngdengca doeh tie hah na panuek awh hoeh maw.
\q1 
\v 6 A kâoupnae hah kalvan totouh a pha teh,
\q2 a lû ni tâmai hah ka phat nakunghai,
\q1 
\v 7 A payungpaei patetlah a yungyoe kahmat vaiteh,
\q2 ahni kahmawtnaw pueng ni na maw ao telah ati awh han.
\q1 
\v 8 Mang patetlah yout kahmat vaiteh, hmawt mahoeh toe.
\q2 Karum e mang patetlah yout kahma e patetlah ao han.
\q1 
\v 9 Ahni kahmawt e mit ni vah hmawt mahoeh toe.
\q2 Hoeh pawiteh, hmuen ni hai kuen mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 10 A canaw ni tami ka roedeng minhmai kahawi hah tawng awh vaiteh,
\q2 a kut hoi hnopai hah bout a bankhai han.
\q1 
\v 11 A hrunaw teh nawcanae thaonae hoi akawi han.
\q2 Hateiteh, vaiphu dawk a ikhai han.
\q1 
\v 12 A pahni dawk kahawihoehe a radip.
\q2 A lai rahim vah a hro nakunghai,
\q1 
\v 13 Pasoung laipalah a pâkuem.
\q2 A kâko dawkvah a hro nakunghai,
\q1 
\v 14 A rawca teh, a vonthung vah a ui vaiteh,
\q2 tahrunsue lah a kangcoung han.
\q1 
\v 15 A tawnta e hnopai hah padoun vaiteh bout a palo han.
\q2 Cathut ni a von thung hoi a tâkhawng pouh.
\q1 
\v 16 Tahrun sue hah a pahap teh,
\q2 tahrun lai ni a ma a thei han.
\q1 
\v 17 Kalawng e palang, khoitui hoi maito sanutui kamkak vaiteh,
\q2 ka lawng e hmawt mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 18 A tawk e thaw ni a coung sak han ei,
\q2 von paha nahanelah hno mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 19 Karoenaw hah a ceitakhai hoi, a coungroe teh,
\q2 Ama ni a sak hoeh e im hah a lawp.
\q1 
\v 20 A lung thung hoi roumnae hah a panue hoeh dawk.
\q2 A ngai e hno buet touh boehai cawi mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 21 A ca hanelah a pek e banghai awm hoeh.
\q2 Hatdawkvah a nawmnae ni kasaw awm mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 22 A nawm lahun nah kângairu vaiteh,
\q2 ama taranlahoi kângairu patawpoung e kut dawk a pha han.
\q1 
\v 23 A von a paha lahun nah Cathut ni
\q2 a lungkhueknae hmai hah ahni koe a tha poeh han.
\q2 A ca lahun nah a lathueng vah lungkhueknae kho a rak pouh han.
\q1 
\v 24 Sum e senehmaica teh, a yawng takhai han ei,
\q2 rahumpala ni pawkkayawng lah a ka awh han.
\q1 
\v 25 Pala teh a phawk, a tak dawk hoi a tâco pouh.
\q2 Loukloukkaang e a hmo hah hmue thung hoi a tâco.
\q2 Takikatho poung e a lathueng vah a pha.
\q1 
\v 26 Runae pueng teh ama hanelah pâtung lah ao.
\q2 Tami ni patawi hoeh e hmai ni be a kak vaiteh,
\q2 a im dawk kaawm e pueng ama hoi a kak han.
\q1 
\v 27 Kalvannaw ni a payonnae hah a pâpho han,
\q2 talai ni ama hah a taran han.
\q1 
\v 28 A im e hnopainaw hah be kahmat vaiteh,
\q2 a lungkhueknae hnin dawk hnokahawinaw
\q2 hah tui patetlah a lawng han.
\q1 
\v 29 Hetheteh Cathut koehoi tamikathoutnaw ni a coe hanelah ao.
\q2 Cathut ni a coe hane râw a pouk pouh e doeh telah a ti.
\c 21
\s1 Job ni Zophar a pathung
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi Job ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Ka lawk he kahawicalah na thai pouh haw,
\q2 Hetheh nangmouh lungmawng nahanelah awmseh.
\q1 
\v 3 Ka dei navah panguep awh ei,
\q2 be ka dei hnukkhu hoi na panuikhai awh vai nei.
\q1 
\v 4 Ka phuenangnae heh tami tarannae lah maw ao.
\q2 Hottelah awm pawiteh, bang kecu dawk maw, ka lung a saw thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 5 Na khen awh haw, kângairu awh naseh.
\q2 Na pahni hah tabuem awh.
\q1 
\v 6 Ka pouk nah ka pâyaw
\q2 takinae ni ka kâha a uek sak.
\q1 
\v 7 Bang kecu dawk maw tamikathoutnaw ni a matawng totouh a hring awh teh,
\q2 thaonae dawk bahu ao han vaw.
\q1 
\v 8 A ca catounnaw hah amamae mithmu vah a kung acaksak awh,
\q2 amamae miphun hah amamae hmalah acaksak awh.
\q1 
\v 9 A imnaw hah takinae thung hoi a hlout teh,
\q2 Cathut e sonron hah ahnimae a lathueng bawt boihoeh.
\q1 
\v 10 Maitotan ni cati tu laipalah awm boihoeh.
\q2 Maitomanu ni ca khe laipalah awm boihoeh.
\q1 
\v 11 Saringhu patetlah a canaw a tâco sak teh,
\q2 a canaw teh a lam awh.
\q1 
\v 12 Tamawi hoi ratoung kueng laihoi la a sak awh,
\q2 Tamawi e a lawk dawk hoi a lunghawi awh.
\q1 
\v 13 Hringnawmnae hoi atueng aloum sak awh teh
\q2 dongdengca dawk phuen vah a cei awh.
\q1 
\v 14 Hateiteh, Cathut koe
\q2 na cettakhai yawkaw,
\q2 na lamthung panue hane heh ka ngai awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 15 Athakasaipounge, a thaw ka tawk pouh hane teh apimaw,
\q2 Ama koe ka ratoum navah ahawinae bangmaw ka mek telah ati awh.
\q1 
\v 16 A tawn awh e hno hah amamae kut dawk kaawm e ka tang nahoeh,
\q2 tami kathoutnaw khokhangnae teh, kaimouh koehoi kahlatpoung la ao.
\q1 
\v 17 Tamikathoutnaw e hmaiim teh, bangmaw atuhoitu a due teh,
\q2 amamae rawkphainae teh, bangmaw atuhoitu a pha.
\q2 Lungmathoenae hah Cathut ni a lungkhueknae dawk hoi lawk ouk a ceng boimaw
\q1 
\v 18 Kahlî dawk e cakong patetlah ao teh,
\q2 kahlî ni palek e vaikong patetlah ao awh.
\q1 
\v 19 Cathut ni a canaw hanelah, payonpakai nahan a ta telah a ti.
\q2 Panuethai awh nahanelah, ahnimouh teh ama ni patho naseh.
\q1 
\v 20 A ronae hah a mit hoi hmawt sak awh,
\q2 Athakasaipounge lungkhueknae manang hah net sak awh.
\q1 
\v 21 Bangkongtetpawiteh, a thapa akuep totouh atueng baw sak lah o teh,
\q2 ama a rawk hnukkhu hoi a im teh, banglahai tho hoeh.
\q1 
\v 22 Karasang lah kaawm e hai lawkcengkung Cathut teh
\q2 apinimaw panuenae a cangkhai thai han.
\q1 
\v 23 Lungmawngcalah hoi karoumcalah ao nah koe,
\q2 tami buet touh a thao lahun nah a due.
\q1 
\v 24 A sanunaw hai sanutui abuem awh teh,
\q2 a hrunaw hai rakhing hoi akawi.
\q1 
\v 25 Tami alouke buet touh, a nawmnae roeroe awm laipalah,
\q2 lungmathoe nalaihoi a due.
\q1 
\v 26 Vaiphu dawk reikâvan lah a i roi,
\q2 tangraet ni muen a kayo.
\q1 
\v 27 Khenhaw! na pouknae naw hah ka panue.
\q2 Ka lan hoeh poung e kai dawk
\q2 sak han na noe e hah ka panue.
\q1 
\v 28 Nâmaw bawi im teh a o,
\q2 nâmaw tamikathoutnaw khosaknae
\q2 rim teh ao telah na ti awh.
\q1 
\v 29 Kahlawng ka cet e hah na pacei boihoeh na maw.
\q2 Mitnoutnae naw hah na panuek awh hoeh maw
\q1 
\v 30 Tamikathoutnaw teh, lawkcengnae hnin hanelah
\q2 pouk tangcoung e lah ao awh.
\q2 Lungkhueknae hnin nah tâcokhai lah ao awh han,
\q2 tie hah na panuek hoeh maw
\q1 
\v 31 Apinimaw a hmaitung vah na lamthung hah hawihoeh atipouh han.
\q2 Apinimaw a sak e hah a patho han.
\q1 
\v 32 Hateiteh, phuen koe ceikhai lah ao teh,
\q2 phuen hah meng kountouk hanelah ao.
\q1 
\v 33 Ayawn dawk e kacoumnaw hah,
\q2 ahnimouh hanlah, a radip vaiteh, tami pueng ni a kâbang han.
\q2 A hmalah touklek hoeh e ka cet tangcoungnaw patetlah
\q2 taminaw pueng a duksawn han telah a ti.
\q1 
\v 34 Hottelah namamae pahni dawk laithoe pou ao lahun nah,
\q2 bangtelamaw hrawnghrang lawk hoi
\q2 lung khuet na pahawi thai awh han, telah a ti.
\c 22
\s1 Eliphaz lawk
\p 
\v 1 Teman tami Eliphaz ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Tami teh Cathut hanelah a cungkeinae a tawn thai han namaw,
\q2 A lungkaang e hai ama hanelah doeh cungkeinae ao.
\q1 
\v 3 Tamikalan lah na onae hah, Athakasaipounge, a lungkahawi sak e lah ao han namaw
\q2 Toun han awm laipalah na sak e na lamthung hah ahni hanelah a meknae ao han namaw
\q1 
\v 4 Ama na taki kecu dawk maw na toun teh,
\q2 lawkcengnae dawk na kâenkhai.
\q1 
\v 5 Na hawihoehnae hah a len poung teh,
\q2 pout laipalah na payonnae kecu dawk nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 6 A khuekhaw awm laipalah na hmaunawngha e hno hah na man pouh teh,
\q2 caici lah kaawm e hnicu hah na la pouh.
\q1 
\v 7 Tha ka tawn e koe, nei hane tui hah na poe hoeh teh,
\q2 von kahlamnaw hanelah vaiyei hah na pasoung pouh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Hateiteh, tami athakaawme ni ram a coe teh,
\q2 a thung vah bari kaawm e tami ni kho a sak awh.
\q1 
\v 9 Lahmainu hah kut caici lah na ceisak awh teh,
\q2 manu ka tawn hoeh e naranaw e kut hah na khoe pouh awh.
\q1 
\v 10 Hatdawkvah na tengpam e karap ni na kalup teh,
\q2 puennae ni rucatnae na poe awh.
\q1 
\v 11 Na hmu thai hoeh nahanelah,
\q2 hmonae hoi tuikalen poung ni muen a khu awh.
\q1 
\v 12 Kalvan arasang nah koe, Cathut awm hoeh namaw
\q2 Karasangpoung e âsinaw hah khenhaw! banghloimaw arasang.
\q1 
\v 13 Nang ni, Cathut ni bangmaw a panue,
\q2 Hmonae hloilah lawk a ceng thai maw.
\q1 
\v 14 A hmu thai hoeh nahanelah, katha poung e tâmai ni a ramuk teh,
\q2 kalvan lathueng lah a kâhlai, telah na ti.
\q1 
\v 15 Tamikathoutnaw ni karawk e lam karuem dawk
\q2 meng na cei han namaw
\q1 
\v 16 Apimaw atueng kuep hoehnahlan vah la e lah kaawm niteh,
\q2 apini a ung e maw tuikalen ni a la.
\q1 
\v 17 Cathut koe, na cettakhai yawkaw,
\q2 Athakasaipounge ni ahnimouh hanelah bangmaw a sak thai telah ati awh.
\q1 
\v 18 Hateiteh a imnaw hah hnokahawi hoi akawi sak.
\q2 Hateiteh tamikathout e khokhangnae teh, kai koehoi kahlatpoung lah ao.
\q1 
\v 19 Tamikalan ni a hmu teh, a lunghawi.
\q2 Yonnae ka tawn hoeh e ni dudamkungnaw hah a panuikhai awh.
\q1 
\v 20 Ka tarannaw teh, raphoe katang lah ao teh,
\q2 kacawie naw hah hmai ni a kak han.
\q1 
\v 21 Ama koe kâpanuek sak nateh, karoumcalah awm,
\q2 haw hoi nang hanelah hnokahawi a tâco han.
\q1 
\v 22 Pahren lahoi amae kâko hoi ka tâcawt e hringnae na cangkhai e hah dâw haw.
\q2 Na lungthin thungvah amae lawk hah kahawicalah kuem.
\q1 
\v 23 Athakasaipounge, koevah na ban pawiteh, kangdout thai e lah o han.
\q2 Na payonpakai e hah na im dawk hoi kahlatpoung lah na takhoe han.
\q1 
\v 24 Nange sui teh, vaiphu dawk na ta han.
\q2 Ophir sui hah sawkca thung e, sadinaw patetlah na pâtung han.
\q1 
\v 25 Athakasaipounge teh,
\q2 nange sui hoi aphu kaawm e ngun lah ao han.
\q1 
\v 26 Hottelah Athakasaipounge dawkvah na lunghawi han.
\q2 Cathut koe lah na khet han toe.
\q1 
\v 27 Ama koe na ratoum vaiteh, na thai pouh han.
\q2 Na lawkkam hah na kuep sak han.
\q1 
\v 28 Hno buet touh na kâcai vaiteh, nama hanelah caksak lah ao han.
\q2 Hot patetvanlah na lamthung dawk angnae ni a tue han.
\q1 
\v 29 Na tâkhawng navah tawmrasang e lah na o han telah na ti han.
\q2 Hottelah kârahnoum e hah ama ni a rungngang han.
\q1 
\v 30 Ka yon hoeh e hah a rungngang han.
\q2 Na kut thoungnae hoi rungngang lah ao han, telah a ti.
\c 23
\s1 Job Eliphaz a pathung
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi Job ni a pathung teh.
\q1 
\v 2 Sahnin hai ka phuenangnae a patawpoung.
\q2 Ka kâhram lawi vah ka kut ni thayung awm hoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 3 Oe, ama teh nâ lah maw ao tie hah ka panue vaiteh,
\q2 a tahungnae koe ka phat haw pawiteh.
\q1 
\v 4 A hmalah ka kong heh ka phakhai vaiteh,
\q2 ka pahni teh na lawkpanuesaknae hoi a kawi han ei.
\q1 
\v 5 Na pathungnae lawk hah ka panue vaiteh,
\q2 kai koe a dei hane hah ka thaipanuek han ei.
\q1 
\v 6 Ka lentoe e hnotithainae hoi na taran han namaw
\q2 Na taran mahoeh, ka kong hah hoe na pouk pouh han doeh.
\q1 
\v 7 Hawvah ama hoi tamikalan ni pouk thai awh vaiteh,
\q2 lawkcengkungnaw koehoi yungyoe ka hlout han toe.
\q1 
\v 8 Khenhaw! hmalah ka cei, hateiteh ama la awm hoeh.
\q2 Hnuklah bout ka ban eiteh, ama teh ka hmawt thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 9 Avoilae kut hoi a tawk navah ama teh ka khen thai hoeh.
\q2 Aranglae kut dawk a kamlang toteh ama hah ka hmawt thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 10 Hateiteh, ka dawn e lamthung hah ama ni a panue.
\q2 Na tanouk toteh sui patetlah ka tâco han.
\q1 
\v 11 A khok dawk ka khok ni kacakcalah a kamtung teh,
\q2 a lamthung hah phen laipalah ka dawn.
\q1 
\v 12 A pahni dawk hoi kâpoelawk hah ka cettakhai hoeh.
\q2 A pahni dawk hoi ka tâcawt e lawk hah
\q2 ka panki e rawca hlak hai ka pâtung.
\q1 
\v 13 Hateiteh, ama teh buet touh lah ao dawkvah,
\q2 apinimaw a dum thai han.
\q2 A hringnae ni a sak han a ngai e pueng hah a sak.
\q1 
\v 14 Kai hanelah a pouk e hah a sak.
\q2 Ama dawk hot patet e hah moikapap ao.
\q1 
\v 15 Hatdawkvah, a hmalah o e hah ka taki.
\q2 Hetheh ka pouk navah ama ka taki.
\q1 
\v 16 Cathut ni ka lung a pout sak teh,
\q2 Athakasaipounge hah na taki sak.
\q1 
\v 17 Hatei, hmonae dawk hoi na kapek hoeh teh,
\q2 ka hma lae hmonae kadung poung e dawk na ramuk hoeh.
\c 24
\q1 
\v 1 Bangkong maw atuengnaw heh Athakasaipounge ni
\q2 a hro hoeh vaw,
\q2 ama kapanueknaw ni
\q2 amamae ahnin hah a hmu thai awh hoeh vaw.
\q1 
\v 2 Tangawn ni khori hah a puen awh.
\q2 Saringnaw hah a lawp awh teh ama hanelah a paca awh.
\q1 
\v 3 Naranaw e la hah a pâlei pouh awh teh,
\q2 lahmai e maitotan hah lawkkamnae lah a pangen pouh awh.
\q1 
\v 4 Tami kavoutthoupnaw hah lamthung a phen sak awh.
\q2 Ram thung e karoedengnaw hah pâkhueng teh, kâhro hoi ao awh.
\q1 
\v 5 Thingyeiyawn ramke dawk e la patetlah,
\q2 rawca tawng hanelah, thaw tawk han lah a cei awh.
\q2 Amamouh hoi a canaw hanelah ram ni ca hane rawca a tâco sak.
\q1 
\v 6 Law dawk e saringnaw e rawca hah a pâkhueng teh,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw e misurpaw hah a pâtung awh.
\q1 
\v 7 Khohna e awm laipalah karum khodai caici lah a i awh.
\q2 Pâding nah kâkhu hane tawn awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Mon dawk kho ka rak e ni cupkâkasu lah a pâsin teh,
\q2 a phui nahanelah lungsongpui a kângue awh.
\q1 
\v 9 A na pa kaawm hoeh e camo teh, a manu e sanu hoi a pâphei sak.
\q2 Karoedengnaw hah amamae hno hah a pâhung sak.
\q1 
\v 10 Karoedengnaw, hah caici lah ao sak awh.
\q2 A von kahlamnaw koe e cabong hah a la pouh awh.
\q1 
\v 11 Ayânaw im vah satui hah a kuen awh teh,
\q2 misurpaw katin nalaihoi tui a kahran awh.
\q1 
\v 12 Khopui thung vah hmenghmeng a due awh teh,
\q2 a hramki awh. Hmâ a ca awh teh, hringnae hah a kaw awh.
\q2 Hateiteh, Cathut ni a ratoum awh e hah pato hoeh.
\q1 
\v 13 Angnae hah taranlahoi tarankathawnaw hah ao.
\q2 A lamthung hah panuek awh hoeh teh,
\q2 angnae lamthung hah ngai awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 14 Tamikathetnaw ni angnae dawk hoi a thaw awh teh,
\q2 karoedengnaw hoi kavoutthoupnaw hah a thei awh.
\q2 Karum e tami tamru patetlah ao awh.
\q1 
\v 15 Ayâ yu yonkhai hane mit ni khohmo a ngaihawi.
\q2 Minhmai a hro teh, apini na hmawt mahoeh telah a pouk.
\q1 
\v 16 Kanîthun lah mitnout a ta e im hah karum lah a muk awh teh,
\q2 angnae hah panuek awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 17 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ahnimouh hanelah teh,
\q2 amom hah duenae tâhlip patetlah ao.
\q2 Tami ni panuek awh boipawiteh,
\q2 takikatho poung e duenae tâhlip doeh ati awh han.
\q1 
\v 18 Tui hoi karanglah pâyo sak lah ao awh han.
\q2 Talai dawkvah coe hane thoebo lah ao han.
\q2 Hatdawkvah, apihai misur takha lamthung koe lah kamlang mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 19 Kawmpoi khumbei kâan e ni tadamtui a kamyawt sak.
\q2 Hot patetvanlah, phuen ni yonnae ka sak e hah a payawp awh.
\q1 
\v 20 Camo im ni a pahnim awh vaiteh,
\q2 tangraet ni katuipoung lah a ca awh han.
\q1 
\v 21 Bangkongtetpawiteh, cakaroe e hah a rektap teh,
\q2 lahmainu hanelah hnokahawi lah awmhoeh.
\q1 
\v 22 Hateiteh, Cathut ni athaonae hoi,
\q2 tami athakaawme taminaw e lamthung hah a raphoe pouh.
\q2 Hring hane kamcenglah a panue hoeh nakunghai, Ama ni a thaw sak.
\q1 
\v 23 A kângue hane a poe teh, hawvah a kâhat sak.
\q2 A mit teh ahnimae lamthung dawk ao.
\q1 
\v 24 Vai touh hoi tawm lah ao teh, hat hnukkhu hoi a kahma awh.
\q2 Rahnoum sak la ao teh, ayânaw patetvanlah a kâhmo van han. Cavui patetlah a ke awh.
\q1 
\v 25 Hot patetlah awm hoeh pawiteh,
\q2 apini maw na laithoe a tithai han.
\q2 Ka dei e heh bang hoeh e lah
\q2 ka coung sak thai e na o awh maw telah a ti.
\c 25
\s1 Bildad lawk
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi Shuhi tami Bildad ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Uknae hoi takinae teh amae naw doeh.
\q2 Hmuenrasang dawkvah roumnae naw a sak.
\q1 
\v 3 A ransanaw hah apinimaw a touk thai han.
\q2 Apie lathueng maw na angnae hah tâcawt laipalah ao boi.
\q1 
\v 4 Bangtelamaw Cathut e hmalah tami a lan thai han.
\q2 Hoeh pawiteh, bangtelamaw napui ni khe e hah a thoung thai han.
\q1 
\v 5 Thapa patenghai ang laipalah, âsinaw hai amae mithmu vah
\q2 thoung awh hoeh pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 6 Pâri hoi tangraet rumram lah kaawm e taminaw natawng teh
\q2 bangtelamaw hoe thoung thai han vaw, telah ati.
\c 26
\s1 Job ni Bildad a pathung
\p 
\v 1 Hatei Job ni a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Hnotithainae ka tawn hoeh e teh, bangtelamaw na kabawp,
\q2 thaonae ka tawn hoeh e kut teh, bangtelamaw na rungngang thai.
\q1 
\v 3 Lungangnae ka tawn hoeh e teh, bangtelamaw na toun thai,
\q2 tami moikapap koevah kalan e pouknae hah bangtelamaw na poe thai.
\q1 
\v 4 Api koe maw lawk teh na pâpho pouh.
\q2 Apie muitha maw nama koe ka phat.
\q1 
\v 5 Tami kadout hah a pâyaw teh, tui rahim vah ao teh,
\q2 haw vah kaawm e naw hoi a pâyaw awh.
\q1 
\v 6 A hmalah duenae caici lah ao.
\q2 Rawkphainae ni ramuknae tawn hoeh.
\q1 
\v 7 Kalvan teh ahrawnghrang dawk a kangdue.
\q2 Talai hai ahrawnghrang dawk a kâbang.
\q1 
\v 8 Katha poung e tâmai dawk tui hah mek a racut teh,
\q2 a rahim e tâmai hah kâbawng awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 9 A bawitungkhung e hmalah a ramuk teh,
\q2 a lathueng vah tâmai a tabo sak.
\q1 
\v 10 Angnae hoi hmonae langri a ta nahanelah
\q2 tui dawk a langri a ruen pouh.
\q1 
\v 11 Kalvan toenae khom a kâhuet teh,
\q2 a tounnae hah kângai lah a ru.
\q1 
\v 12 A hnotithainae lahoi tuipui a thaw sak.
\q2 Bahu lahoi tûilî hah thawk a kapek.
\q1 
\v 13 A muitha lahoi kalvan a pathoup sak.
\q2 Kamleng e khorui hai a kut hoi a sak.
\q1 
\v 14 Khenhaw! hetnaw heh lamthung nueng kamtawngnae doeh.
\q2 Ahnimouh koe e thai awh e hrolawk teh, banghloimaw a thoung.
\q2 Hateiteh, keitat hnotithainae hah, apinimaw a panue thai.
\c 27
\s1 Job ni a lannae a kampang
\p 
\v 1 Job ni a dei e hah bout a patawp teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Cathut ni ka lannae, na la pouh teh,
\q2 Athakasaipounge, ka hringnae ka pataw sak e teh a hring e patetlah,
\q1 
\v 3 Ka thung e a thakaawm sak e Cathut e kâha teh
\q2 ka hnong dawk ao thung pueng teh,
\q1 
\v 4 Ka pahni ni kathoute lawk dei mahoeh.
\q2 Ka lai ni dumnae tâcawtsak mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 5 Na lan awh tie hah ka dei hane savisava doeh.
\q2 Ka due totouh ka lannae heh khoeroe ka pahnawt mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 6 Ka lannae heh kacakcalah ka kuet teh, kahmat sak mahoeh.
\q2 Ka hring thung pueng ka lungthin ni kama yon na pen mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 7 Ka taran hah tamikathout patetlah awm awh naseh.
\q2 Kai na taranlahoi ka kangdout e hah tami kalan hoeh lah awm awh naseh.
\q1 
\v 8 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tami kahawihoehe naw ngaihawinae teh, banghai nahoeh.
\q2 Moi ka tawn nakunghai Cathut ni a hringnae lat pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 9 a lathueng vah runae a pha torei teh,
\q2 a cingounae hah Cathut ni a thai pouh han maw.
\q1 
\v 10 Athakasaipounge, lah amahoima a lunghawi han namaw,
\q2 Cathut hah pou a kaw han namaw.
\q1 
\v 11 Cathut e kut hoi a sak e hah na dei pouh vai.
\q2 Athakasaipounge, koevah kaawm e hah ka hrawk mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 12 Hot teh abuemlah ni na hmu katang awh.
\q2 Hottelah pawiteh, bangkongmaw bang hoeh e dawk pou na panui awh.
\q1 
\v 13 Hetteh, Cathut koehoi tamikathoutnaw coe hanelah ao.
\q2 Tami kahnephnapnaw e a coe e raw.
\q2 Athakasaipounge, koehoi a hmu awh e teh,
\q1 
\v 14 a catounnaw a kamphung nakunghai tahloi hanelah doeh ao.
\q2 A canaw ni vonhlam hoi kho a sak awh han.
\q1 
\v 15 Kaawm rae naw teh, duenae dawk pakawp la ao awh han.
\q2 Lahmainaw ni khuikapkhai mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 16 Vaiphu patetlah ngunnaw ka pâtung nakunghai,
\q2 tangdong patetlah hnopai ka pâtung nakunghai,
\q1 
\v 17 a pâtung thai han. Hateiteh, tamikalan ni a khohna han,
\q2 kayonhoehnaw ni ahnie ngun hah a kârei awh han.
\q1 
\v 18 Bomba patetlah im a sak teh,
\q2 ramveng ni rim a sak e patetlah doeh ao.
\q1 
\v 19 Tami ka tawn poung ni a due torei teh, pakawp e lah awm mahoeh.
\q2 A mit a padai nah teh koung a kahma toe.
\q1 
\v 20 Takithopoung e ni ahni teh tuikalen patetlah a la.
\q2 Karum lah tûilî ni a kahma sak.
\q1 
\v 21 Kanîtholah kahlî ni a palek teh awmhoeh toe.
\q2 A onae hmuen koehoi a palek.
\q1 
\v 22 Pek e awm laipalah ama khuehoi a palek.
\q2 A thasainae thung hoi koung a kahma han.
\q1 
\v 23 Taminaw ni a kuttabawng sin han.
\q2 Terawseh tet awh vaiteh aonae koehoi a pâlei awh han.
\c 28
\s1 Lungangnae kong dawk Job ni lawk a dei
\q1 
\v 1 Ngun tainae tangkom ao katang,
\q2 sui sôlêinae a hmuen hai ao.
\q1 
\v 2 Sum teh talai dawk hoi la e lah a o,
\q2 rahum teh talung dawk hoi thawng e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 3 Tami ni hnonae dawk a pout sak teh,
\q2 a hmuen kingkadi e pueng totouh a tawng awh,
\q2 duenae tâhlip hoi hmonae thung vah
\q2 a cei awh teh a tawng awh.
\q1 
\v 4 Tami a ohoehnae koe vah tangkom a tai teh,
\q2 khok ni a pahnim e hmuennaw hah
\q2 tami hoi a kâhlanae hmuen koe a bang awh teh,
\q2 pou a kâhuet awh.
\q1 
\v 5 Talai e tui dawk hoi rawca tâconae lah a o,
\q2 a rahim lah teh hmai ni talai a kâthungsak e patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 6 Hote talungnaw teh, sapphire talung a phukaawm
\q2 a tâconae a kung lah ao. Sui kanuinaw hai ao.
\q1 
\v 7 Hote lamthung teh tavanaw ni panuek hoeh,
\q2 mataw e mit ni hai hmawt hoeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Ka po e sendek ni hai coungroe hoeh,
\q2 ka matheng e sendek hai cet boihoeh.
\q1 
\v 9 Talung dawk tami ni kut a toung teh,
\q2 mon hah a kung koehoi pakhuppathan lah dek a palei.
\q1 
\v 10 Lungsongpui hah a kavi teh, ravohong a sak teh,
\q2 a mit hoi a phukaawm poung e hno hah a hmu.
\q1 
\v 11 Tui ka phuek e hah a tawng teh,
\q2 kâhrawk e hnonaw hah angnae dawk a tâcokhai.
\q1 
\v 12 Hateiteh, nâ lah maw lungangnae hmuthainae teh,
\q2 nâ lah maw panuethainae hmuen hah ao.
\q1 
\v 13 Aphu onae tami ni panuek hoeh,
\q2 Tami onae ram dawk hmu thai lah awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 14 Kadunge ni kai koe awm hoeh telah a ti,
\q2 talî ni kai koe awm hoeh a ti.
\q1 
\v 15 Sui hoi ran thai lah awm hoeh,
\q2 aphu teh ngun hoi hai bangnue thai lah awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 16 Ophir talung phu kaawm ni hai phat thai hoeh,
\q2 aphu kaawm poung e onyx hoi
\q2 sapphire ni hai phat thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 17 Sui hoi talung phukaawm ni hai phat thai hoeh,
\q2 sui kathoung hoi hai thung thai lah awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 18 Koral hoi jasper hai deipan han kamcu hoeh,
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lungangnae phu teh,
\q2 Rubies talung hlak hai a phu hoe a rasang.
\q1 
\v 19 Ethiopia ram e topaz talung phu kaawm ni phat thai hoeh,
\q2 sui kathoung ni hai aphu onae phat thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 20 Hot patet lae lungangnae teh,
\q2 nâhoi maw a tho,
\q2 thoumthainae hmuen teh nâ lah maw ao.
\q1 
\v 21 Kahringnaw pueng e mit ni a khet teh hmawt thai hoeh,
\q2 kalvan e tavanaw ni hai a tawng teh hmawt thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 22 Rawkphainae hoi duenae ni a dei awh e kamthang hah,
\q2 ka hnâ ni a thai telah ati awh.
\q1 
\v 23 Cathut ni a lamthung hah a panue pouh teh,
\q2 hmuen hai a panue
\q1 
\v 24 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ama ni talai apout totouh a khet,
\q2 kalvan rahim pueng hah a hmu.
\q1 
\v 25 Kahlî teh khing hane hoi,
\q2 tui teh bangnuenae hoi bangnue hane,
\q1 
\v 26 kho a rak nahanelah lamthung a sak pouh teh,
\q2 khoparitnae hoi sumpapalik nahane lamthung a sak pouh navah,
\q1 
\v 27 Lungangnae a hmu teh a pâpho,
\q2 a caksak teh a tawng.
\q1 
\v 28 Tami koe khenhaw! BAWIPA takinae teh lungangnae doeh,
\q2 kahawihoehe ceitakhai e teh
\q2 panuethainae doeh telah a ti.
\c 29
\s1 Job ni a lannae a kampangkhai
\p 
\v 1 Job ni a dei lawk hah bout a patawp teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Oe ka loum tangcoung e a kum hoi thapa naw dawk bout kaawm haw pawiteh,
\q2 Cathut ni na kountouknae a hnin patetlah
\q1 
\v 3 ka lû dawk hmaiim a ang teh,
\q2 a angnae dawk hoi hmonae ka tapuet thai navah,
\q1 
\v 4 Ka roung takhangnae a tueng,
\q2 ka im dawk Cathut hoi kâhuikonae tueng,
\q2 hatnae patetlah bout kaawm haw pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 5 Athakasaipounge, kai koe na okhai e hoi,
\q2 ka canaw ka teng vah petkâkalup lah ao awh navah,
\q1 
\v 6 Ka ceinae lamthung dawk maito sanutui a lawng,
\q2 lungsongpui ni kai hanelah satui pou a lawng sak navah,
\q1 
\v 7 khopui kâennae longkha koe ouk ka cei navah,
\q2 thongma dawk ouk ka tahungnae koe ka ceikhai navah,
\q1 
\v 8 Thoundounnaw ni na hmu awh teh, a kâhro awh.
\q2 Kacuenaw ni a thaw awh teh a kangdue awh.
\q1 
\v 9 Bawinaw ni lawk dei hane pahni a cakuep awh.
\q2 A kut hoi pahni a tabuem awh.
\q1 
\v 10 Bawinaw hai lawkkamuem lah duem ao awh teh,
\q2 a lai teh adangka dawk rapkâbet pouh.
\q1 
\v 11 A hnâ ni a thai torei teh, yawhawi na poe awh.
\q2 A mit hoi a hmu awh torei teh na panuikhai awh.
\q1 
\v 12 Bangkongtetpawiteh, karoedengnaw hah ka rungngang teh
\q2 na pa hoi kabawmkung ka tawn hoeh e naw hah ouk ka kabawp.
\q1 
\v 13 Kahmatkatanaw e yawhawinaw hah, ka lathueng vah a pha.
\q2 Lahmainaw e lungthin hah lunghawinae la ka sak sak.
\q1 
\v 14 Lannae hah ka khohna teh,
\q2 ka lannae teh angkidung hoi bawilakhung patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 15 Mitdawnnaw hanelah mit lah ka o teh,
\q2 khokkhemnaw hanelah khok lah ka o.
\q1 
\v 16 Karoedengnaw, hanelah na pa lah ka o teh,
\q2 ka panue hoeh e naw e lawk hai ka ngai pouh.
\q1 
\v 17 Tamikathoutnaw e a no hah ka khoe pouh teh,
\q2 a hâ hoi a kei e hah ka rasa pouh.
\q1 
\v 18 Hottelah ka tabu thung ka due vaiteh,
\q2 ka hninnaw teh sadi patetlah ka pung sak han.
\q1 
\v 19 Tui aonae koe vah ka tangphanaw ka payang vaiteh,
\q2 ka kangnaw dawk karum khodai tadamtui ao han.
\q1 
\v 20 Ka bawilennae teh ka thung vah bout a katha teh,
\q2 ka pala teh ka kut dawk a tha hoi a kawi han.
\q1 
\v 21 Taminaw ni na ring teh na rabui awh.
\q2 Ka khokhangnae dawk duem ao awh.
\q1 
\v 22 Ka dei hnukkhu hoi banghai dei awh hoeh toe.
\q2 Ka dei e teh ahnimouh koe tadamtui patetlah a bo.
\q1 
\v 23 Khotui patetlah na ring awh teh, a hnukteng e kho ka rak e patetlah
\q2 kakawpoung lah pahni a ang awh.
\q1 
\v 24 Ka panuikhai pawiteh yuem awh mahoeh.
\q2 Ka minhmai a angnae teh, hmonae lah awm sak awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 25 Ahnimouh hane lamthung ka rawi teh,
\q2 kahrawikung patetlah ka tahung.
\q2 Hottelah ransanaw thung vah siangpahrang patetlah kho ka sak.
\q2 A lung ka mathoutnaw lungpahawi e patetlah ka o.
\c 30
\q1 
\v 1 Hatei, atuteh kai hlak ka camo e naw ni
\q2 Kai na pathoe awh.
\q2 A napanaw hah kai ni ka panuet teh,
\q2 kaie tuhu ka ring e uinaw koe patenghai bawk van hoeh.
\q1 
\v 2 A thaonae hah kai hanelah bangmaw cungkeinae kaawm.
\q2 A thayung tawn awh hoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 3 Takangnae hoi voutthoup dawk a kamsoe awh teh,
\q2 kahrawngum kingdinae hmuen koe tang a yawng awh.
\q1 
\v 4 Pho um e angmai hna a la awh teh,
\q2 samphokung e a tangpha hah rawca hanelah a tai awh.
\q1 
\v 5 Ahnimouh teh, tami koehoi pâlei awh teh,
\q2 tamru patetlah a hramsin awh.
\q1 
\v 6 Tangkom thung hoi lungngoum thung o hanelah doeh ao awh.
\q2 Talai hoi talung kâko dawk ao awh.
\q1 
\v 7 Caprapum vah a hram awh teh,
\q2 pâkhingum vah a tabo awh.
\q1 
\v 8 Ahnimouh teh tamipathu e canaw doeh.
\q2 Bang pato patang hoeh e canaw doeh.
\q2 Ram thung hoi hrek e naw doeh.
\q1 
\v 9 Atu teh la lah na sak awh hanelah ka o toe.
\q2 Na pathoe e lah ka o toe.
\q1 
\v 10 Na panuet awh teh kai hoi kâhlat lah na o awh.
\q2 Ka minhmai na tamthawi awh.
\q1 
\v 11 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lirui hah a rasu awh teh, na ka pacekpahlek awh.
\q2 Ka hmalah kammoumrui a rasu awh.
\q1 
\v 12 Kaie aranglah nawsainaw a kangdue teh, ka khok hah a phen awh.
\q2 A rawkphainae lamthung hah kai taranlahoi a sak awh.
\q1 
\v 13 Ka lamthung hah a raphoe awh.
\q2 Kai ka tâlaw nahanelah a kâyawm awh.
\q2 Ahnimouh kâhruetcuet ka poe hane apihai awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 14 Ka kaw poung e kâko dawk hoi a tho awh teh,
\q2 ningkatim rahim vah na kalup awh.
\q1 
\v 15 Takithopoung e ka lathueng vah a pha.
\q2 Bari lah ka onae hah kahlî patetlah a pâlei awh.
\q2 Ka tawn e naw hah tâmai patetlah a kahma.
\q1 
\v 16 Ka kângairunae ni ka hringnae teh a rabawk toe.
\q2 Ka khangnae hninnaw ni khak na kuet.
\q1 
\v 17 Karum lah ka hru hah koung a thut teh,
\q2 ka tharui patawnae ni roum thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 18 Ka patawpoung e ni hnicu hoi kayo e patetlah na kayo teh,
\q2 angki lahuen patetlah na katek.
\q1 
\v 19 Tangdong dawk na tâkhawng teh,
\q2 hraba hoi vaiphu patetlah ka o toe.
\q1 
\v 20 Nama koe ka hram, hateiteh, na pato hoeh.
\q2 Ka kangdue teh na khet.
\q1 
\v 21 Hatei, kai hanelah ka pahngawpahrak e lah na o.
\q2 Na kut thasainae ni na taran.
\q1 
\v 22 Kahlî dawk na tawm teh,
\q2 a lathueng vah na kâcui sak.
\q1 
\v 23 Bangkongtetpawiteh, nama ni duenae dawk na ceikhai hane hah ka panue.
\q2 Hringnae katawnnaw pueng hanelah,
\q2 na pouk pouh tangcoung e im dawkvah.
\q1 
\v 24 BAWIPA ni a kut a dâw torei teh,
\q2 a kâhei nakunghai, banglah tho hoeh toe. A raphoe torei teh,
\q2 a hram nakunghai hawinae awm hoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 25 Runae ka kâhmonaw hanlah ouk ka ka nahoehmaw.
\q2 Karoedengnaw hanlah lungreithai hoi kaawm boihoeh maw.
\q1 
\v 26 Hateiteh, hawinae ka tawng navah,
\q2 hno kahawihoehe hah ka lathueng vah a pha.
\q2 Angnae ka ring navah hmonae a pha.
\q1 
\v 27 Ka lungthin a tâsue teh roum thai hoeh.
\q2 Ka khangnae hninnaw ni na tho sin.
\q1 
\v 28 Panuinae koelah tho hoeh niteh, lungmathoe koelah ka cei.
\q2 Kamkhuengnaw rahak vah, ka kangdue teh, kabawpnae ka hei teh ka hram.
\q1 
\v 29 Kahrawnguinaw e hmaunawngha lah ka o.
\q2 Kalauk tavanaw hoi huiko lah ka o.
\q1 
\v 30 Ka vuen teh hoehoe a tamang teh kai koehoi a bo,
\q2 Ka hrunaw teh puenghoi a kâan
\q1 
\v 31 Ka ratoung teh ka lungmathoenae lah a coung,
\q2 ka tamawi teh kâlawk lah a coung.
\c 31
\q1 
\v 1 Ka mit ni lawkkamnae a sak,
\q2 Bang kecu dawk maw tangla hah ka mit ni a khet han.
\q1 
\v 2 Hatdawkvah, lathueng lae Cathut koehoi ka coe hane hoi,
\q2 Athakasaipounge koehoi a parâw e teh bangmaw.
\q1 
\v 3 Tamikathoutnaw raphoe teh,
\q2 payonpakainae ka sak e naw rawkphainae nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 4 Ama ni ka lamthung hah a hmu teh,
\q2 ka khokhnuk pueng hai be a touk nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 5 Kalan hoeh e lah ka hring pawiteh, hoeh pawiteh,
\q2 dumyennae hoi ka khok a hue rang pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 6 Kânging e yawcu khingnae hoi na khing haw,
\q2 Cathut ni ka lannae hah a panue thai han.
\q1 
\v 7 Ka pahni ni lamthung phen boipawiteh,
\q2 ka mit hoi ka hmu e patetlah lungthin ka tawn pawiteh,
\q2 ka kut dawk ka tamang e kâbet pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 8 Cati na tu sak haw, ayâ louk ni cat naseh,
\q2 ka a hane be phawng naseh.
\q1 
\v 9 Napui ni ka lungthin na pasawt payon pawiteh,
\q2 ka imri e takhang arulahoi ka tuet pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 10 ka yu ni ayâ hane cakang phawm naseh.
\q2 Ayâ ni ipkhai naseh.
\q1 
\v 11 Bangkongtetpawiteh, hot teh kathoute lah awm vaiteh,
\q2 lawkcengnae koe tâcokhai hanelah
\q2 kamcu e payonnae lah ao han.
\q1 
\v 12 Bangkongtetpawiteh, raphoe hanelah hmai ni a kak e lah ao han,
\q2 Ka tawn e abuemlah be kahmat e lah ao han.
\q1 
\v 13 Ka sannu sanpanaw ni kai koe a phuenang awh navah,
\q2 noutna laipalah kaawm pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 14 BAWIPA a thaw torei teh, kai ni bangmaw ka sak han.
\q2 Na toun navah bangtelamaw ka pato han.
\q1 
\v 15 Von thung vah kai ka sak e ni,
\q2 ahnimouh hai sak hoehnamaw,
\q2 ama ni manu e von thung rei na sak hoehnamaw.
\q1 
\v 16 Karoedengnaw, e a ngainae hah poe laipalah kaawm pawiteh,
\q2 lahmainaw lung ka pout sak pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 17 naranaw hah canei hane rei laipalah,
\q2 kama dueng ouk ka cat pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 18 Hateiteh, ahni hah ka nawca hoi a na pa patetlah ka okhai,
\q2 anu e von thung hoi lahmai patetlah ka khetyawt toe.
\q1 
\v 19 Tami bangpatet hai hnicu laipalah kadout e hoi,
\q2 tami karoedengnaw kâkhu han ka tawn hoeh e
\q2 ka hmawt boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 20 A lungthin hoi kai yawhawi na poe hoeh teh,
\q2 ka tumuen hoi phu ka bet sak hoehpawiteh,
\q1 
\v 21 longkha koe e kabawpnae ka hmu torei teh,
\q2 naranaw taranlahoi ka kut ka dâw pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 22 ka kut heh ka loung dawk hoi kârakhing naseh,
\q2 ka lounghrunaw hah kâkhoe naseh.
\q1 
\v 23 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut koehoi rawkphainae teh,
\q2 kai hanelah taki a tho poung, bangkongtetpawiteh,
\q2 a lentoenae teh ka khang thai mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 24 Sui hah ngaihawinae hoi ka sak teh,
\q2 nang teh ka lungmawngnae doeh,
\q2 telah suikathoung koe ka dei boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 25 ka kut hoi ka tawk e ni moikapap a hmu teh,
\q2 ka tawntanae a len poung dawkvah,
\q2 lunghawinae ka tawn boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 26 kanî a sei torei ka pouk teh,
\q2 a angnae hoi ka cet e thapa hah a lawkpui lah ka pouk teh,
\q1 
\v 27 hottelah ka lungthin hah arulahoi a pasawt teh,
\q2 ka pahni ni ka kut pahnuem pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 28 het haiyah lawkcengnae hmuen koe
\q2 phakhai han kamcu e payonnae doeh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lathueng la kaawm e
\q2 Cathut hah pahnawt e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 29 Ka hmuhma e lathueng vah, rawkphainae a pha navah,
\q2 ka lunghawi teh, a lathueng vah kathout e ka hmu navah,
\q2 kai kâoup pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 30 Ka pahni ni yonnae dawk thoseh,
\q2 a hringnae hah thoebo hane kâpoe hanelah
\q2 ka pasoung hoeh e thoseh,
\q1 
\v 31 Lukkareiim dawk taminaw ni a teng vah kaawm e
\q2 apimaw von ka hlam e kaawm boi,
\q1 
\v 32 Hateiteh, imyin ni lam vah roe boi hoeh,
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, kahlawng ka cet naw hanelah
\q2 ka im vah tho ouk ka paawng pouh.
\q1 
\v 33 Adam patetlah kâtapoenae hah ka ramuk teh,
\q2 ka payonpakainae hah ka lungtabue thung ka hrawk pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 34 Tamimaya a pap poung dawkvah, ka taki teh
\q2 ka imthungnaw dudamnae ka taki kecu dawkvah,
\q2 duem ka o e hoi alawilah tâco thai hoeh e lah kaawm pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 35 Oe, kapanuekkhaikung buet tabang awm haw pawiteh,
\q2 khenhaw! hetteh kaie kutnout doeh, Athakasaipounge ni,
\q2 na pato haw pawiteh, kai na katarannaw ni
\q2 cauk dawk thut haw pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 36 Ka loung dawk hoi roeroe ka sin vaiteh,
\q2 bawilukhung patetlah ka kâmuk han ei .
\q1 
\v 37 Ka khokhnuknaw pueng hai ama koe ka pâpho han,
\q2 bawi patetlah ama teh ka hnai han ei.
\q1 
\v 38 Ka ram ni kai taranlahoi a hram teh,
\q2 laikawk kongnaw ni cungtalah khui awh pawiteh,
\q1 
\v 39 aphu poe laipalah a pawnaw hah ka ca teh,
\q2 katawnkungnaw hringnae sung sak e lah kaawm boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 40 hottelah cang yueng lah pâkhing paw naseh,
\q2 Catun yueng lah phovainaw paw naseh telah a ti,
\q2 Job e lawk a pâpout toe.
\c 32
\s1 Elihu ni Job e a huinaw a oun
\p 
\v 1 Job ni amahoima tamikalan a kâti dawkvah, tami kathum touh ni Job pathung awh hoeh toe.
\v 2 Hottelah Barakel e capa Elihu, Buz tami Ram catoun Elihu teh pueng hoi a lungkhuek. Cathut hlak amahoima tamikalan a kâti dawkvah, Job koe a lungkhuek.
\v 3 Job e a hui kathum touh koehai a lungkhuek. Bangkongtetpawiteh, Job hah na payon atipouh eiteh, bout pathung nahane panuek awh hoeh.
\v 4 Ahnimouh teh, ama hlak vah kacuehnawn lah ao. Elihu ni Job koevah lawk dei hanelah meng a ring.
\v 5 Elihu ni hetnaw kathum touh e pahni dawk hoi pathung nahan awm hoeh tie hah a panue torei teh, a lung puenghoi a khuek.
\p 
\v 6 Hottelah, Barakel e capa Elihu, Buz tami ni hettelah a pathung. Kai teh kum kanaw teh, nangmouh teh na kumcue poung awh toe. Hatdawkvah, na taki awh teh, ka pouknae hai ka dei ngam hoeh.
\b
\q1 
\v 7 Kum ni dei naseh, kum moikapap ni
\q2 lungangnae cangkhai naseh ka ti.
\q1 
\v 8 Hateiteh, tami e thung kaawm e muitha,
\q2 Athakasaipounge kâha hah
\q2 panuethainae kapoekung lah ao.
\q1 
\v 9 Tamikalannaw ni hoe lungangnae awm hoeh
\q2 kum kacuenaw ni lannae hoe panuethainae awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 10 Hatdawkvah, na thai pouh awh haw,
\q2 kai ni hai ka pouknae ka pâpho han.
\q1 
\v 11 Khenhaw! na lawknaw hah ka thai teh,
\q2 dei hanelah ao telah na pouk lahun nah
\q2 na panuesaknae hah ka panue toe.
\q1 
\v 12 Kahawicalah na thai pouh haw
\q2 lawk ka pathung thai e
\q2 Job e a lung pan ka cai sak e, nangmouh thung dawk
\q2 buet touh hai na awm awh hoeh maw.
\q1 
\v 13 Lungangnae ka hmu toe, tami nahoeh niteh,
\q2 Cathut ni ama teh a tâ han na tet awh payon vaih.
\q1 
\v 14 A lawknaw ni rep na tâdue hoeh
\q2 nangmae lawk patetlah ahni teh bout ka pathung mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 15 A lung a pout awh teh, pathung awh hoeh toe,
\q2 lawkkamuem ao awh toe.
\q1 
\v 16 Lawk a dei awh hoeh toung dawkvah,
\q2 ka ring rah, bangkongtetpawiteh,
\q2 pathung toung laipalah duem a kangdue awh.
\q1 
\v 17 Kai ni hai kama hane ka pathung van han,
\q2 ka pouknae teh ka pâpho van han.
\q1 
\v 18 Bangkongtetpawiteh, lawk hoi ka kawi teh,
\q2 ka thung e muitha ni dei hoeh laipalah,
\q2 na awm sak thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 19 Ka thung lae hah misurtui tâconae
\q2 kâko kaawm hoeh e patetlah ao.
\q2 Misurtui um katha patetlah kâbawng hane coungkacoe ao toe.
\q1 
\v 20 Ka kâha a tâco thai nahanelah, lawk ka dei han,
\q2 Ka pahni roeroe ka ang vaiteh ka pathung han.
\q1 
\v 21 Apipi nakunghai, kapeknae kamnue sak hoeh nahanlah
\q2 tami bangpatet hai ka oup hoeh nahanlah ka ratoum.
\q1 
\v 22 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tami oupnae hah ka thoum hoeh,
\q2 telah nahoeh pawiteh, kasakkung ni
\q2 palang na lat payon vaih.
\c 33
\s1 Elihu ni Job a oun
\q1 
\v 1 Hateiteh Job, pahren lahoi ka dei e heh na thai pouh haw,
\q2 ka lawk ka dei e heh na ngai pouh haw.
\q1 
\v 2 Atu ka pahni ka ang teh,
\q2 ka pahni dawk hoi ka lai ni lawk a dei.
\q1 
\v 3 Ka lawknaw heh kalan e ka lungthung hoi a tâco teh,
\q2 ka pahni ni kathounge panuenae a pâpho.
\q1 
\v 4 Cathut e Muitha ni na sak teh,
\q2 Athakasaipounge kâha ni hringnae na poe.
\q1 
\v 5 Na pathung thai pawiteh na pathung haw,
\q2 ka hmalah na lawk hah bout kâpouk haw.
\q1 
\v 6 Atangcalah tetpawiteh, kai teh Cathut hmalah lawk ka dei pouh e lah ka o,
\q2 kai hai vaiphu hoi sak e lah ka o van.
\q1 
\v 7 Kai dawk kaawm hoeh e takinae ni na takisak roeroe han,
\q2 nahoeh pawiteh, ka kut heh na tak dawk ri poung mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Ka hnâthainae dawk na dei toung dawkvah,
\q2 na lawk teh ka thai toe.
\q1 
\v 9 Na lawk ka ek hoeh dawkvah ka thoung,
\q2 Yonnae ka tawn hoeh, payonpakainae kai dawk awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 10 Hatei, kai taran nahane atueng kahawi a hmu teh,
\q2 a taran patetlah na pouk.
\q1 
\v 11 Ka khok hah hlong na buet teh,
\q2 ka lamthung pueng hah a khet na ti.
\q1 
\v 12 Khenhaw! hivah nang teh na lan hoeh, na pathung han,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut teh tami hlak a len.
\q1 
\v 13 Ama ni a lawk bangpatethai noutna mahoeh telah,
\q2 bangkongmaw ama hah na pathoe.
\q1 
\v 14 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut ni lam alouklah hoi lawk a dei thai,
\q2 hatei, tami ni hmawt panuek hoeh.
\q1 
\v 15 Karum a i navah vision dawk mat ka ip e,
\q2 ikhun dawk a i lahun nah,
\q1 
\v 16 Tami e hnâkâko hah a ang sak teh,
\q2 amae cangkhainae hah a cak sak.
\q1 
\v 17 A sak e thung dawk hoi tami a ban teh,
\q2 a kâoupnae dawk hoi hro lah ao thai nahanelah,
\q1 
\v 18 a hringnae hah tangkom thung hoi a kountouk teh,
\q2 tahloi hoi duenae thung hoi a hringnae a rungngang.
\q1 
\v 19 Tami teh a ikhun dawk patawnae hoi a yue teh,
\q2 a hrunaw hah puenghoi patawnae hoi a pataw sak.
\q1 
\v 20 Hottelah a hringnae ni rawca a panuet teh,
\q2 katuipounge rawca hai a hringnae ni a panuet.
\q1 
\v 21 A takthai a kamsoe teh,
\q2 kamnuek boihoeh e a hrunaw hah a kamnue.
\q1 
\v 22 A hringnae ni tangkom hah a hnai teh,
\q2 a hringnae ni kathetkung hah hoehoe a hnai.
\q1 
\v 23 Ahni hanelah laiceinaw awm boipawiteh,
\q2 kâponae kasakkung 1000 thung dawk tami buet tabang awm pawiteh,
\q2 tami ni amae lannae hah a hmu sak thai nahanelah.
\q1 
\v 24 Ama ni tami hah a pahren teh,
\q2 tangkom thung bonae koehoi ama teh a rungngang han,
\q2 ratangnae buet touh ka hmu toe telah a ti.
\q1 
\v 25 A takthai teh camo e takthai patetlah bout ao vaiteh,
\q2 a nawcanae patetlah bout ao han.
\q1 
\v 26 Cathut koevah a ratoum vaiteh, ama teh a lathueng vah a lunghawi han,
\q2 a minhmai hah lunghawi hoi a hmu han,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, ama ni tami teh a lannae hoi bout a ban sak.
\q1 
\v 27 A huikonaw a khet teh ka yon toe,
\q2 tamikalan hah ka rawp sak toe,
\q2 hot teh kai hanelah banghai cungkeinae awmhoeh telah a ti.
\q1 
\v 28 Tangkom thung e a hringnae hah a ratang vaiteh,
\q2 a hringnae ni angnae a hmu han.
\q1 
\v 29 Khenhaw! Cathut ni hete hnopueng heh,
\q2 vai hni, atangcalah vai thum totouh tami koe a sak.
\q1 
\v 30 Hringnae angnae ni a ma hah a tue thai nahanelah,
\q2 a hringnae tangkom thung hoi a tâco sak.
\q1 
\v 31 Na hnâpakeng nateh, Job na thai pouh haw,
\q2 duem awm haw ka dei han.
\q1 
\v 32 Dei hanelah na tawn pawiteh, na pathung haw, dei haw,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, yon ngaithoum hane na ngaikhai poung.
\q1 
\v 33 Telah nahoeh pawiteh, na thai pouh haw,
\q2 duem awm haw, lungangnae na dei pouh han.
\c 34
\s1 Elihu ni Cathut lannae a pâpho
\q1 
\v 1 Elihu ni rekrek a pathung teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Nangmouh a lungkaangnaw ka lawk heh thai awh,
\q2 Nangmouh panuenae katawnnaw, na hnâpakeng awh.
\q1 
\v 3 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka kâko ni rawca atuinae a patek e patetlah,
\q2 hnâ ni lawk hah a tanouk van.
\q1 
\v 4 Maimouh roeroe ni lannae teh, kârawi awh haw sei.
\q2 Ahawinae hah bangmaw tie hah maimae thung hoi panuek awh haw sei.
\q1 
\v 5 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Job ni kai teh ka lan,
\q2 hateiteh, Cathut ni ka lannae a la
\q1 
\v 6 Ka lannae e kong dawk ka laithoe han na maw,
\q2 kâtapoenae ka tawn hoeh nakunghai ka hmâ teh,
\q2 ka dam thai hoeh e doeh toe, telah a ti.
\q1 
\v 7 Panuikhainae hah tui patetlah ka net e,
\q2 Job patetlah apimaw kaawm.
\q1 
\v 8 Payonnae kasaknaw hoi kamyawng e,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw hoi ka cet e apimaw kaawm.
\q1 
\v 9 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut koe lunghawi e heh,
\q2 tami ni banghai hawinae awm hoeh telah ati toe
\q1 
\v 10 Hatdawkvah, panuethainae katawnnaw na thai pouh haw,
\q2 kathoute ka sak e teh, Cathut hanelah roeroe coung thai hoeh,
\q2 yonnae ka sak e teh, Athakasaipounge hanelah khoeroe coung thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 11 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tami hah a sak e patetlah ama ni a patho han,
\q2 tami pueng a tawksak e hoi kamcu lah tawkphu kamcu lah a poe han.
\q1 
\v 12 Cathut ni kahawihoeh poung lah sak mahoeh,
\q2 nahoeh pawiteh, Athakasaipounge ni lannae teh,
\q2 khoeroe kamlang takhai mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 13 Apinimaw ama teh talai e thaw a poe,
\q2 talai van pueng heh apinimaw ama a uk sak.
\q1 
\v 14 Ama ni tami teh a ngainae awm hoeh pawiteh,
\q2 kai e hringnae kâha hah lat boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 15 Takthai pueng reirei a kahma han
\q2 tami teh vaiphu lah bout a ban han.
\q1 
\v 16 Thaipanueknae na tawn awh pawiteh, Kâlawk pawlawk heh thai awh haw.
\q1 
\v 17 Lannae ka hmuhma e ni a uk han namaw,
\q2 Kalan ni teh athakaawme hah, yon na pen thai namaw.
\q1 
\v 18 Nang teh banghai cungkeinae na awm hoeh telah, siangpahrang koe dei pouh han.
\q1 
\v 19 Hateiteh, ahni ni bawi hai kapeknae tawn hoeh,
\q2 Tami tangreng hoi roedeng hoi kapeknae ka tawn hoeh e doeh.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, abuemlahoi amae kutsaknaw doeh.
\q1 
\v 20 Karumsaning tawkkadek a due awh teh,
\q2 taminaw pueng hah a kâhuet awh teh, koung a kahma awh,
\q2 tami athakaawme hai tami e kut laipalah be kahmat lah a la pouh.
\q1 
\v 21 Bangkongtetpawiteh, a mit teh tami e lamthung dawk ao teh,
\q2 a khoktakan puenghai be a hmu,
\q1 
\v 22 Yonnae kasaknaw, amamouh kâhro nahane hmuen awmhoeh,
\q2 duenae tâhlip hai awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 23 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut e hmalah lawkceng hane cei hanelah,
\q2 tami e kong bout pouk hane ama ni panki hoeh.
\q1 
\v 24 A kung rek khei ngai laipalah athakaawme taminaw hah koung a tâtueng han,
\q2 ahnimae hmuen dawk tami alouke o nahanelah ka poe han.
\q1 
\v 25 Hatdawkvah, ahnimouh ni a sak e pueng hah a panue teh,
\q2 karum vah ama ni a tâkhawng teh koung a kâbawng.
\q1 
\v 26 Tami ni a hmu thai e hmuen koe,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw patetlah a hem awh.
\q1 
\v 27 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ama hah a kamlang takhai awh,
\q2 a lamthung hah pouk raw pouk awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 28 Hottelah karoedengnaw e lawk hah a hmalah a pha,
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh rektapnaw e lawk hah a ma ni a thai.
\q1 
\v 29 BAWIPA ni roumnae a poe torei teh, apinimaw rucatnae a poe thai han,
\q2 a minhmai a hro torei teh, apinimaw a hmu thai han,
\q2 miphun buet touh taranlahoi thoseh, tami buet touh taranlahoi thoseh,
\q1 
\v 30 Tamikahawihoeh e ni a uk hoeh nahanlah,
\q2 telah nahoeh pawiteh, tami pueng koung kaithi payon han.
\q1 
\v 31 Tami ni Cathut koehoi tounnae ka hmu toe.
\q2 Kai teh hawihoehnae ka sak mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 32 Ka hmu hoeh e hah na cangkhai haw, Payonnae hah ka sakpayon pawiteh, bout ka sak mahoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 33 Na lawkkamnae na pahnawt dawkvah, na sak e boiboelah na pathung han na maw.
\q2 Kai ni na hoeh, nang ni roeroe na kârawi han.
\q2 Hatdawkvah, na panue e hah deih.
\q1 
\v 34 Panue thainae katawnnaw hoi,
\q2 ka lawk ka thai e lungkaangnaw ni kai koe vah,
\q1 
\v 35 Job ni panuenae tawn laipalah lawk hah a dei,
\q2 a lawk hah lungangnae kaawm hoeh e naw doeh telah a dei awh.
\q1 
\v 36 Oe Job heh a pout totouh tanouknae lah awm yawkaw naseh,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, lawk pathungnae hah tamikathoutnaw lawk pathungnae patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 37 Bangkongtetpawiteh, a yonnae dawk taranthawnae a thap sin,
\q2 maimouh koevah, kut tambei teh,
\q2 Cathut taranlahoi lawk a pap telah a ti.
\c 35
\q1 
\v 1 Hahoi Elihu ni a pathung e teh,
\q1 
\v 2 Heteheh, a lan telah na pouk maw,
\q2 Cathut lannae hlak ka lan telah na dei maw.
\q1 
\v 3 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka yonnae hah pap boipawiteh,
\q2 hot teh, nang hanelah bangmaw a hawinae, meknae hoe ka hmu telah na ti.
\q1 
\v 4 Nama koe kaawm e naw hoi na pathung han.
\q1 
\v 5 Kalvan lah moung nateh khenhaw! khenhaw!
\q2 nang hlak hoe ka rasang e tâmainaw hah,
\q1 
\v 6 Yonnae na sak pawiteh, ama taranlahoi bangmaw hoe na kuepcing sak,
\q2 nahoeh pawiteh kâtapoenae hah pap pawiteh, ama hanelah bangmaw na sak,
\q1 
\v 7 Tamikalan lah na awm pawiteh, ama hah bangmaw na poe,
\q2 Nahoeh pawiteh, ama ni na kut dawk hoi bangmaw a hmu.
\q1 
\v 8 Na hawihoehnae ni nang patetlah kaawm e tami hah a ratet,
\q2 na lannae ni tami capa buet touh a ratet.
\q1 
\v 9 Hnephnap e a pap kecu dawkvah a hramki awh,
\q2 athakaawme taminaw e rektapnae kecu dawkvah,
\q2 kabawpnae a panki hoi a hram awh.
\q1 
\v 10 Hateiteh, apinihai nâmaw kasakkung Cathut,
\q2 karum lah la sak han ka poe e hah ao telah dei awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 11 Talai e sarang hlak hai apinimaw na cangkhai awh.
\q2 Kalvan e tava hlak lung na ang sak awh.
\q1 
\v 12 Tamikathoutnaw a kâoup kecu dawk,
\q2 hawvah a hram awh ei, pathung awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 13 Banghai bang hoeh e lawk hah Cathut ni khoeroe thai mahoeh,
\q2 Athakasaipounge, ni hai banglahai noutna mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 14 Ama teh na hmawt hoeh telah na dei nakunghai,
\q2 amae hmalah lannae ao teh, ama teh na ring raw na ring han.
\q1 
\v 15 Bangkongtetpawiteh, atuvah a lungkhueknae dawk hoi na rek hoeh niteh,
\q2 pathunae hnonaw pueng hah pâkuem hoeh.
\q1 
\v 16 Hatdawkvah, Job ni a khuekhaw awm laipalah,
\q2 a pahni a ang teh, panuenae laipalah lawk a pap sak.
\c 36
\s1 Elihu ni Cathut hawinae a pâpho
\q1 
\v 1 Elihu ni hettelah bout a dei,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Na ngaithoum awh ei,
\q2 na hmusak awh han rah.
\q2 Cathut yueng lah lawk dei hane ka tawn rah.
\q1 
\v 3 Ka panuenae hah ahlanae koe e ka la han rah,
\q2 lannae hah kasakkung koe kamnue sak han.
\q1 
\v 4 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka lawknaw heh ayawmyin lah khoeroe ao hoeh dawkvah,
\q2 panuenae kuep katawnkung teh nang koe ao.
\q1 
\v 5 Khenhaw! Cathut teh a thasai eiteh, apihai dudam hoeh.
\q2 Ama teh athao teh thonae thaipanueknae hoi a kawi
\q1 
\v 6 Tamikathoutnaw hah pâhlung hoeh.
\q2 Hateiteh, hnephnap e naw hah lannae a poe.
\q1 
\v 7 Tamikalan teh khen laipalah awm hoeh,
\q2 hateiteh, siangpahrang hah bawitungkhung dawk yungyoe hanelah a tahung sak teh,
\q2 ahnimouh teh tawmrasang e lah ao awh.
\q1 
\v 8 Puenghoi kacaklah katek e lah o awh teh,
\q2 rucat khangnae rui hoi katek e lah awm boipawiteh,
\q1 
\v 9 Kâtapoenae hoi a sak e hah
\q2 lungpata lahoi sakyoenae hoi a kamnue sak.
\q1 
\v 10 Cangkhainae koelah hna a ang sak teh,
\q2 yonnae dawk hoi bout a ban nahane kâ a poe.
\q1 
\v 11 Lawkngai laihoi amae thaw tawk awh pawiteh,
\q2 hnopai tawnta e dawk nawm awh vaiteh,
\q2 hnin, thapa, kum naw hah lunghawinae hoi a loum sak han.
\q1 
\v 12 Hateiteh, lawkngai awh hoeh pawiteh,
\q2 tahloi hoi kahmat ka ta awh vaiteh,
\q2 panuenae tawn laipalah due awh han.
\q1 
\v 13 Hateiteh, tamikathout e lungthin ni lungkhueknae a pâtung teh,
\q2 ama ni a katek torei teh, kabawpnae hei hanelah hram awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 14 A nawca nah a due awh teh,
\q2 a hringnae hah tami kahawihoehnaw hoi rei a pout.
\q1 
\v 15 Ama ni tami ka roedeng hah reithainae thung hoi a hlout sak.
\q2 Hnephnapnaw hno lahoi a hnâ a ang sak.
\q1 
\v 16 Takithopoung e kângairunae thung hoi ama ni a hlout sak han.
\q2 Khori kaawm hoeh e, hmuen kakawpoung koe,
\q2 tawntanae dawk a kâenkhai han,
\q2 na caboi teh tawntanae hoi kawi vaiteh a poum sak han.
\q1 
\v 17 Hateiteh, tamikathoutnaw ni hmu han kamcu e lawkcengnae hoi,
\q2 na kâvan teh, lawkcengnae hoi lannae ni na kuet.
\q1 
\v 18 Lungkhueknae ao dawkvah, kâhruetcuet.
\q2 Nahoeh pawiteh, vai touh hemnae dawk ama ni na cetkhai payon vaih.
\q2 Bangkongtetpawiteh, ratangnae kalen poung ni na hlout nahane na kabawm mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 19 Na tawntanae hoi na thaonae, na bahu onae pueng ni,
\q2 na kângairunae dawk hoi na hlout sak han na maw.
\q1 
\v 20 Karum hah kâuepkhai hanh.
\q2 Taminaw karum dawk kahmanae tueng lah ao.
\q1 
\v 21 Yonnae dawkvah kamlang hoeh nahanlah kâhruetcuet,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, reithai khangnae hlak hai na kârawi e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 22 Khenhaw! Cathut teh hnotithainae dawk hoi tawmrasang e lah ao.
\q2 Apinimaw ama patetlah a cangkhai boi.
\q1 
\v 23 Apinimaw a lamthung hah a poukkhai boi.
\q2 Apinimaw na sak e hah na payon telah atipouh boi.
\q1 
\v 24 A tawk e thaw hah len sak hanelah pahnim hanh,
\q2 tami ni la lah a sak awh e hah.
\q1 
\v 25 Tami pueng ni a hmu awh teh, tami ni ahlanae koehoi a radoung awh.
\q1 
\v 26 Khenhaw! Cathut teh a lentoe poung,
\q2 maimouh ni panuek thai awh hoeh.
\q2 Kumnaw hai panue thai lah awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 27 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tui ka ca e naw hah,
\q2 a lathueng lah a sawn teh, tuikahu kaawm e patetlah kho a rak sak.
\q1 
\v 28 Hote tâmai dawk hoi a rak sak teh,
\q2 tami e lathueng vah, kho a nan sak.
\q1 
\v 29 Tâmai ka tabawk e hoi ama ni a lathueng vah a ramuk e khoparitnaw hah,
\q2 apinimaw a panue thai han.
\q1 
\v 30 Khenhaw! a lathueng vah a angnae pheng a tue sak teh,
\q2 kadung poung e tuipuinaw hah pheng a ramuk.
\q1 
\v 31 Bangkongtetpawiteh, hete hnonaw lahoi, tami hah lawk a ceng teh,
\q2 rawca koung kakhoutlah a poe.
\q1 
\v 32 Na kut hah sumpapalik hoi a ramuk teh,
\q2 ka hanelah kâ a poe.
\q1 
\v 33 Khoparit e ni a kamnue sak teh,
\q2 saringnaw ni hai tûilî a thonae hah a kamnue sak.
\c 37
\q1 
\v 1 Hete hnonaw ni hai ka lungthin a pâyaw sak teh,
\q2 lung paluekpaluek ati sak.
\q1 
\v 2 Khoparit pawlawk hah kahawicalah thai haw,
\q2 a pahni dawk hoi ka tâcawt e ka cairing e naw hah.
\q1 
\v 3 Kalvan rahim pueng a tha teh,
\q2 a angnae teh talai apout touh.
\q1 
\v 4 Hahoi lawk a tâco teh, a lentoenae lawk hah a kampaw sak.
\q2 A lawk a thai awh nakunghai kâhat sak hoeh.
\q1 
\v 5 Cathut ni kângairunae hoi a lawk a kampaw sak,
\q2 a lentoenae hno panue thai awh hoeh e hah a sak.
\q1 
\v 6 Bangkongtetpawiteh, tadamtui koe vah, talai dawk bawt haw telah ati.
\q2 Hot patetlah, athaonae hoi khorak kayoun hoi khorak kapap koehai a dei pouh.
\q1 
\v 7 Tami pueng ni a sak e a panue awh thai nahanelah,
\q2 tami pueng e kut hah mitnout a ta pouh.
\q1 
\v 8 Moithangnaw ni lungngoum thung a kâen awh teh,
\q2 a onae hmuen dawk lengkaleng ao awh.
\q1 
\v 9 Aka lahoi bongparui a tâco teh,
\q2 Atunglah hoi kahlî pâding a tâco.
\q1 
\v 10 Cathut e a kâha ni tui a kamkak sak teh,
\q2 kakawpoung lah kâkadai e tui hah a kamkak sak.
\q1 
\v 11 Tâmai dawk hoi kho a rak sak teh,
\q2 a raeng hoi tâmai a kâhin sak.
\q1 
\v 12 Talaivan pueng dawkvah kâ a poe e naw pueng hah a sak awh nahanelah,
\q2 amae hrawinae dawk hoi a kamlang awh teh, meng a ban awh.
\q1 
\v 13 Hring tounnae dawk thoseh, a ram hane dawk thoseh,
\q2 a lungmanae dawk thoseh, ao sak e doeh.
\q1 
\v 14 Oe Job, hetheh thai haw, duem awm nateh, kangdout haw.
\q2 Kângairu Cathut ni a sak e hah pouk haw.
\q1 
\v 15 Cathut ni ka ang e tâmai hah ang hanelah,
\q2 nâtuek vaimoe a patoun tie hah na panue maw.
\q1 
\v 16 Tâmai a tawmnae hoi panuenae kakueplah ka tawn e ni,
\q2 a sak e kângairunae hah na panue maw.
\q1 
\v 17 Bangdawkmaw na hnicunaw a phubet teh,
\q2 nâtuek maw akalae kahlî ni talai a pâding sak.
\q1 
\v 18 Hlun e rahum hlalang patetlah
\q2 a tha ka sai e kalvan hah ama hoi reirei na phai roi boimaw.
\q1 
\v 19 Ama koe dei awh hanelah na cangkhai awh haw,
\q2 bangkongtetpawiteh, hmonae kecu dawk,
\q2 banghai kârakueng thai awh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 20 Dei han ka ngai telah, ama koe dei hane na maw.
\q2 Tami buetbuet touh dei sak boipawiteh, a payon roeroe han.
\q1 
\v 21 Kahlî a tho teh kalvan hah pin a kâhin sak torei teh,
\q2 tami ni a angnae hah khen thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 22 Atung lahoi sui raimonae patetlah a tâco teh,
\q2 Cathut hoi takitho taluenae lah ao.
\q1 
\v 23 Athakasaipounge, teh hmawt thai hoeh.
\q2 Ama teh ahlawilah hnotithainae a tawn teh,
\q2 a lannae hoi lawkcengnae dawk hnephnapnae awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 24 Hatdawkvah, ama teh tami ni a taki awh.
\q2 A lungkaang e taminaw koe hai,
\q2 kapeknae tawn hoeh telah ati.
\c 38
\s1 BAWIPA ni Job pathunae a kamnue sak
\p 
\v 1 Hottelah BAWIPA ni Job hah bongparui thung hoi a pathung teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Panuenae laipalah e lawk hoi,
\q2 khokhangnae kahmawtsakkung teh apimaw.
\q1 
\v 3 Atuvah tongpatang lah namahoima kârakueng haw,
\q2 lawk na pacei vaiteh na pathung haw.
\q1 
\v 4 Talai ka kamtawng nah nâmaw na o,
\q2 na thai panuek pawiteh na dei pouh haw.
\q1 
\v 5 Apinimaw bangnuenae a panue thai,
\q2 na panue thai na maw.
\q2 Apinimaw bangnuenae a rui hah a lathueng lah a payang.
\q1 
\v 6 Apinimaw adu hah a ung teh
\q2 bang ni maw adu hah a casak.
\q1 
\v 7 Tempalo âsinaw hah cungtalah la a sak awh navah,
\q2 Cathut e capanaw teh lunghawi hoi hram awh hoeh maw.
\q1 
\v 8 Talînaw teh thun thung hoi a tâco navah,
\q2 apinimaw tho a khan sin.
\q1 
\v 9 A hnicu hanelah tâmai ka sak pouh teh,
\q2 a kâkhu hanelah hni lah katha poung e hmonae,
\q1 
\v 10 a langri ka khuen pouh teh,
\q2 tho tarennae ka hruek pouh.
\q1 
\v 11 Hi totouh na tho vaiteh, a hloilah na tapuet mahoeh.
\q2 Hivah na kâoupnae hoi tuicapa hah pout naseh telah ka ti.
\q1 
\v 12 Talai a pout totouh a kuet teh,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw peng a tâco thai nahanelah.
\q1 
\v 13 Na tâco tahma hoi amom heh kâ na poe teh,
\q2 a tâconae hmuen na panue sak boimaw.
\q1 
\v 14 Mitnoutnae rahim vah talai patetlah meilam a sin teh,
\q2 hnicu patetlah a kangdue sak.
\q1 
\v 15 Tamikathoutnaw koehoi angnae hah a la pouh teh,
\q2 a dâw e kut hah a khoe pouh.
\q1 
\v 16 Tuipui a tâconae dawk a kâen boimaw.
\q2 Adungnae bangnue hanelah koung na rip toung maw.
\q1 
\v 17 Duenae takhang hah nang koe a kamnue sak toung maw.
\q2 Nahoeh pawiteh, duenae tâhlip takhang hai na hmu boimaw.
\q1 
\v 18 Talai akawnae naw heh be na panue maw.
\q2 Hetnaw pueng he na panuek pawiteh, na dei pouh haw.
\q1 
\v 19 Nâ lah maw angnae, khosaknae lamthung ao.
\q2 Hmonae a hmuen hai nâ lah maw ao.
\q1 
\v 20 Hot teh khori dawk na hrawi thai teh,
\q2 a lamthung hah na panue thai nahanelah.
\q1 
\v 21 Hatnae tueng dawk na tâco teh,
\q2 nange hnin hah apap poung dawkvah,
\q2 hot teh na panue ngoun vaiyaw.
\q1 
\v 22 Tadamtui pâtungnae hmuen koe na kâen toung maw.
\q2 Roun kamtungnae hmuen te na hmu thoung maw.
\q1 
\v 23 Rucatnae atueng hanelah ka ta e hoi
\q2 tarankâtuk nahane hnin hanelah ka ta e doeh.
\q1 
\v 24 Nâ lae lamthung hoi maw angnae ni pheng a tue teh,
\q2 talai van vah kanîtholah kahlînaw a kâkahei.
\q1 
\v 25 Tui ka poum e a lawngnae ravo hoi,
\q2 keitat lamthung hah apinimaw a sak.
\q1 
\v 26 Apihai a ohoehnae ram hoi
\q2 apihai a ohoehnae kahrawngum dawk khorak sak hane hoi,
\q1 
\v 27 King ka di e talai ni kanaw e phovai a dawnnaw tâco sak hanelah,
\q2 ka poum e khotui a lawngnae lamthung,
\q2 khoparit hoi sumpapalik lamthung apinimaw a kamawng sak.
\q1 
\v 28 Khotui ni a na pa a tawn maw.
\q2 Tadamtui ka bawt e hah apinimaw a khe.
\q1 
\v 29 Apie von dawk hoi maw tui kamkak a tâco.
\q2 Kalvan hoi ka bawt e tadamtui hah apini a khe e na maw.
\q1 
\v 30 Tui hah talung patetlah a te sak teh,
\q2 tui adungnae hai be kamkak.
\q1 
\v 31 Baritca hah na pâkhueng thai teh,
\q2 kangduetaphai rui hah na rathap thai maw.
\q1 
\v 32 Mazzaroth hah amae tueng nah na tâco sak thai maw.
\q2 Latum teh a canaw hoi na ceikhai thai maw.
\q1 
\v 33 Kalvan e caksak e naw hah na panue teh,
\q2 talai heh na uk sak thai maw.
\q1 
\v 34 Kho pueng hoi ka sak e ni na ramuk thai nahanelah,
\q2 tâmai totouh na lawk na cai sak thai maw.
\q1 
\v 35 Sumpapalik e hah nang koe a tho teh,
\q2 hivah ka o telah nang koe dei hanelah na patoun thai maw.
\q1 
\v 36 Apinimaw pouknae dawk lungangnae a poe.
\q2 Apinimaw lungthin hah panuethainae a poe.
\q1 
\v 37 Apinimaw lungangnae hoi tâmai a touk thai han.
\q2 Apinimaw kalvan e tuium rabawk thai han.
\q1 
\v 38 Vaiphu hah a te sak teh,
\q2 tangdong dawk buet touh lah a kâbet toteh,
\q1 
\v 39 a kâkhu dawk hoi a pawp teh,
\q2 kei hanlah a pawp lahun nah,
\q1 
\v 40 Sendek hane rawca tawng pouh hane
\q2 sendektancanaw kaboumlah paca thai maw.
\q1 
\v 41 Vongacanaw vonhlam hoi a kâva teh, Cathut koe a hram awh toteh,
\q2 apinimaw rawca a poe.
\c 39
\q1 
\v 1 Mon dawk e Atha ca khenae tueng hah na panue maw,
\q2 Sayuk ca khenae tueng te na pâkuem thai maw.
\q1 
\v 2 Thapa nâyittouh maw a vawn tie hah na panue thai maw,
\q2 a khenae tueng te na panue thai maw.
\q1 
\v 3 A tabo awh teh a ca a khe,
\q2 a canaw teh a pâ sak.
\q1 
\v 4 A canaw hah a dam awh teh kahrawngum a roung awh.
\q2 A tha ao awh.
\q1 
\v 5 Kahrawng e lanaw hah apinimaw a ngai patetlah a pâ sak.
\q2 Kahrawng e la pennae rui apinimaw a rasu.
\q1 
\v 6 Kahrawng hah apie im lah maw ka sak teh,
\q2 kahrawngum hah api khosak nahanelah maw ka sak.
\q1 
\v 7 Runae ka kâhmo e khopui a dudam teh,
\q2 kahrekkungnaw e hramnae lawk hah noutna pouh hoeh.
\q1 
\v 8 Mon teh a pawngpanae lah ao teh,
\q2 hram kanaw hah a tawng awh.
\q1 
\v 9 Savitan ni nange thaw a tawk ngai han na maw,
\q2 na saring im dawk a roe ngai han na maw.
\q1 
\v 10 Savitan hah a lahuen dawk laikawk kanawknae laphu hah na thueng thai han na maw.
\q2 Na hnuk lae tangkom a paten ngai han na maw.
\q1 
\v 11 A thao poung dawkvah na kâuepkhai maw.
\q2 Na thaw hah ahni dawk na patue thai han na maw.
\q1 
\v 12 Na cakang hah im lah a phu hane hoi,
\q2 cangkatinnae koe cabong pâkhueng sak hanelah,
\q2 na kâuepkhai thai maw.
\q1 
\v 13 Kalauk vâ ni a rathei hah a kâoup nalaihoi ouk a kamphuet,
\q2 hatei a rathei hai a muennaw ni lungmanae a tawn maw.
\q1 
\v 14 Bangkongtetpawiteh, talai dawk a tadui a ceitakhai teh,
\q2 vaiphu dawk a phu a bet sak.
\q1 
\v 15 Tami ni rakkâbawng lah a coungroe thai,
\q2 moithangnaw ni a kâbawng sak thai tie hah panuek hoeh toe.
\q1 
\v 16 A canaw hah a ca hoeh e patetlah puenghoi a rek teh,
\q2 a thaw tawk e a hrawnghrang lah ao e hah bang lahai pouk hoeh.
\q1 
\v 17 Bangkongtetpawiteh, Cathut ni lungangnae a lawp teh,
\q2 thoumthainae hoi pathoup hoeh.
\q1 
\v 18 A rasangnae koe amahoima a kâtawm toteh,
\q2 marang hoi marang dawk kâcui e hah a dudam.
\q1 
\v 19 Marang thaonae hah na poe e na maw,
\q2 a lahuen dawk khoparit hoi na pathoup boimaw.
\q1 
\v 20 Samtong patetlah na pakhi thai maw,
\q2 ahnie hnawng dawk hoi kacaie lawk teh taki a tho.
\q1 
\v 21 Tanghling hah a khok hoi a kaphai teh, a thaonae dawkvah a nawm,
\q2 tarankâtuknae puengcang thung vah karang poung lah a yawng.
\q1 
\v 22 Takithopoung e hah a panuikhai teh, lungpuennae awm boihoeh.
\q2 Hoehpawiteh, tahloi taki hoi ban boihoeh.
\q1 
\v 23 A lathueng vah palabom hah poe a kâroe teh, pala hoi tahroe hah poe a kâhlai.
\q1 
\v 24 Takitho e hoi lungkhuek nah laihoi, mongka lawk ni hai kacakcalah kangdout sak thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 25 Mongka lawk a cai torei teh, awhaw! telah a ti.
\q2 Taran kâtuknae hah ahlanae koehoi a hmui lah a thai.
\q2 Kahrawikungnaw a hramnae lawk hoi târuetâho lawk a thai.
\q1 
\v 26 Cangkhainae lahoi mataw ni a rathei a kadai teh,
\q2 akalah a kamleng thai maw.
\q1 
\v 27 Karasangpoung lah a kamleng teh,
\q2 karasangpoung lah tabu a tuk e hah,
\q2 nang ni kâ na poe e namaw.
\q1 
\v 28 Lungha dawk kho a sak teh,
\q2 karasang e lungha kânguenae rapanim koe ouk a roe.
\q1 
\v 29 Haw hoi a ca hane hah a tuet teh,
\q2 a mit ni ahla poungnae koe e hai a hmu thai.
\q1 
\v 30 A canaw ni thi ouk a du awh teh,
\q2 kadout e moikong onae pueng koe ao awh.
\c 40
\p 
\v 1 Hahoi BAWIPA ni lawk a pathung teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Athakasaipounge, hoi lawk ka oun e ni ama teh a yue han na maw,
\q2 Cathut ma ni pathung yawkaw seh khe, telah atipouh.
\s1 Job ni Cathut a pathungnae
\p 
\v 3 Job ni BAWIPA hah a pathung teh,
\b
\q1 
\v 4 Khenhaw! kai teh banghai cungkeihoehe lah ka o,
\q2 bangtelamaw ka pathung han,
\q2 ka pahni teh ka tabuem toe.
\q1 
\v 5 Vai touh ka dei toung dawkvah, ka pathung mahoeh toe.
\q2 Vai hni touh e teh bout ka dei mahoeh toe telah a ti.
\s1 Cathut ni Job rek a pathung
\p 
\v 6 Hottelah Cathut ni Job hah bongparui thung hoi a pathung teh hettelah a dei:
\b
\q1 
\v 7 Atuvah tongpatang lah coungkacoe awmh.
\q2 Lawk na pacei vaiteh na pathung han.
\q1 
\v 8 Ka lawkcengnae hah na pathung katang han maw,
\q2 na yon hoeh nahanlah yon na pen han maw.
\q1 
\v 9 Cathut patetlah kut na tawn maw,
\q2 ama patetlah pawlawk na cai sak thai maw.
\q1 
\v 10 Taluenae hoi raimonae lah kamthoup haw,
\q2 bawilennae hoi na meihawinae kamthoup.
\q1 
\v 11 Na lungkhueknae e hah tâcawt sak haw,
\q2 Kâoup e pueng hah khen nateh pabawt haw.
\q1 
\v 12 Kâoup e pueng hah khen nateh rahnoum sak haw,
\q2 tamikathoutnaw hah a onae hmuen dawkvah repcoungroe sin awh.
\q1 
\v 13 Vaiphu dawk cungtalah be hrawk awh,
\q2 kâhrawk e hmonae hoi a minhmai hah ramuk awh.
\q1 
\v 14 Hottelah aranglae na kut ni na rungngang thai e hah,
\q2 kai ni hai ka pâpho han.
\q1 
\v 15 Khenhaw! nama patetlah ka sak e Behemoth heh
\q2 maitotan patetlah pho kahring a ca van.
\q1 
\v 16 A keng dawk e thaonae hoi a vonpui dawk e
\q2 tharui hnotithainae hah khenhaw!
\q1 
\v 17 A mai teh sidar thing patetlah a kâroe sak teh,
\q2 a phai dawk e tharuinaw teh a bawk bawk lah ao.
\q1 
\v 18 A hrunaw teh rahum khom patetlah ao teh, a nâhru teh sum khom patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 19 Cathut e lamthung dawk hoi ahni te pasuek e lah a o,
\q2 ahni dueng doeh kasakkung ni tahloi hoi kâhnai sak e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 20 Monnaw ni ca hane a tâco sak,
\q2 hawvah moithangnaw pueng ni a pai awh.
\q1 
\v 21 Lotus thingkung rahim vah a tabo teh,
\q2 lungpum rahim hoi tuinawk dawk hai ouk ao.
\q1 
\v 22 Lotus thingkung tâhlip ni a ngue awh,
\q2 palang rai e sumpakungnaw ni a kalup.
\q1 
\v 23 palang tui teh a len thai,
\q2 hateiteh banglah noutna hoeh,
\q2 apâhni totouh Jordan tui kalen nakunghai a lungmawng.
\q1 
\v 24 A mit hoi a khet lahun nah,
\q2 naphai do thai han namaw.
\c 41
\q1 
\v 1 Leviathan hah hradang hoi alawilah pawk na sawn thai han namaw,
\q2 rui hoi a lai hah a kam dawk na kawm thai maw.
\q1 
\v 2 A hnawng dawk hnâpacap na pacap sak teh,
\q2 Tamboung dawk laikaw na buen sak han na maw.
\q1 
\v 3 Nang koe ka hei vaiteh,
\q2 lawk kanemca hoi lawk a dei han na maw.
\q1 
\v 4 Nang hoi lawkkamnae sak vaiteh,
\q2 yungyoe okhai hanelah na la thai han na maw.
\q1 
\v 5 Tavaca patetlah ahni hoi reirei na pai han na maw.
\q2 Nama e yu lah la hanelah, na pâkhi thai han na maw.
\q1 
\v 6 Na huikonaw ni ama hoi buvennae hah a sak vaiteh,
\q2 hno kayawtnaw koe, ama teh a rei awh han namaw.
\q1 
\v 7 Tahroe donghmo hah a vuen dawk a kawi sak vaiteh,
\q2 tanga kamannaw hah tahroe hoi a lû dawk a kawi sak thai nahoehmaw.
\q1 
\v 8 A lathueng vah a kut toung nateh, tarantuknae hah pahnim hoeh,
\q2 khoeroe bout sak hanh lawi.
\q1 
\v 9 Ama tâ hane ngaihawinae hah a hrawnghrang doeh,
\q2 a mithmu vah a tâ thai hoeh e ao han namaw.
\q1 
\v 10 Ama lungtho sak hanelah apihai a lungtang mahoeh.
\q2 Hottelah pawiteh, apimaw ka hmalah ka kangdout thai han.
\q1 
\v 11 Kai ni ka patho hanelah apinimaw hmaloe na poe,
\q2 kalvan rahim e hnocawngca pueng hah kaie seng doeh.
\q1 
\v 12 A kut khok thoseh, athaonae pueng thoseh,
\q2 a takthai a thaonae, a meihawinae hah ka hrawk pouh mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 13 Alawilae a pho hah apinimaw a rading pouh thai han,
\q2 a tamboung hru bawk hni touh kâpâbawk e hah apinimaw rek a hnai thai han.
\q1 
\v 14 Apinimaw a minhmai takhang hah a paawng thai han,
\q2 takikathopounge a hânaw hah.
\q1 
\v 15 A keng dawk e a pho, a lakepnaw hah a kâoupnae naw lah a o,
\q2 mitnoutnae patetlah kacakcalah khan e lah ao.
\q1 
\v 16 Buet touh hoi buet touh khikkâcat teh,
\q2 a rahak dawk kahlî hai kâen thai hoeh.
\q1 
\v 17 Hotnaw teh buet touh hoi buet touh koung kâkuet teh,
\q2 kapek thai lah awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 18 A hâ tangawn ni angnae a tâco sak teh,
\q2 a mit hah kho nueng kadai e patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 19 A kâko hoi hmaito angnae a tâco teh,
\q2 hmaitali a tangpei.
\q1 
\v 20 A hnawng dawk hoi hmaikhunaw a tâco teh,
\q2 moi thawngnae hlaam dawk ka tangdawk e hoi,
\q2 ka kang e buruk patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 21 A kâha ni hmaisaeinaw a kak teh,
\q2 a pahni dawk hoi hmaito a tâco.
\q1 
\v 22 A lahuen dawk thaonae ao teh,
\q2 a hmalah lungmathoenae hah a len.
\q1 
\v 23 A takthai hoi tharuinaw teh khakkâkuet teh,
\q2 kâtahruet thai hoeh e kacakpounge lah ao.
\q1 
\v 24 A lungthin teh talung patetlah a te,
\q2 Cakang phawmnae a rahim lae talung patetlah a te.
\q1 
\v 25 A thaw torei teh, athakaawme taminaw ni a taki awh,
\q2 a thao e a taki awh dawkvah, ka pathu e patetlah ao awh.
\q1 
\v 26 Ahni koe tahloi ka phat nakunghai tâ thai mahoeh,
\q2 pala, tahroe ni hai tâ thai mahoeh.
\q1 
\v 27 Sum hah cakong patetlah a pouk,
\q2 rahum hah thingke patetlah a pouk.
\q1 
\v 28 Licung ni yawng sak thai mahoeh,
\q2 Talung hoi dêi e hah ahni hanelah teh cakongkung patetlah ao.
\q1 
\v 29 Bongpai hah cakong patetlah a pouk teh,
\q2 pala dawk hoi duenae hah koe a panuikhai.
\q1 
\v 30 A vonpui vuen hah kahran poung e hlaam kâbawng e patetlah doeh a o,
\q2 tangdong um vah cangkatin e seh patetlah a tabo.
\q1 
\v 31 Ka dungpoung e tui hah hlaam patetlah a tangdo sak teh,
\q2 talî kadung poung e hah satuium patetlah a sak.
\q1 
\v 32 A cei tangcoungnae dawk angnae hah a hruek teh,
\q2 tami ni a dungpoung ati e tui hah sampo patetlah a pouk.
\q1 
\v 33 Takinae tawn laipalah, sak e lah ao teh,
\q2 talai van dawk ahni patetlae awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 34 Ka rasang poung e hno pueng hah a khet nah,
\q2 ahni teh kâoup e catoun pueng dawk siangpahrang doeh telah a ti.
\c 42
\s1 Job pankângainae hoi Cathut ni a coenae
\p 
\v 1 Hottelah Job ni BAWIPA hah a pathung teh hettelah a dei.
\b
\q1 
\v 2 Bangpuengpa na sak thai tie hah ka panue,
\q2 na noenae hah ngang thai lah awm hoeh.
\q1 
\v 3 Apimaw kaie panuenae laipalah khokhangnae ka hrawk e hah telah na pacei.
\q2 kai hanelah kângairu poung e lah, ka panue hoeh e ka pâpha e lah ao hah ma.
\q1 
\v 4 Pahren lahoi thai nateh, lawk na dei sak haw.
\q2 Lawk na pacei vaiteh na pathung haw telah na ti.
\q1 
\v 5 Nang teh hnâ hoi dueng doeh na thai rah,
\q2 hatei, atu teh ka mit hoi na hmu toe.
\q1 
\v 6 Hatdawkvah, kama hoi kama ka kâpanuet teh,
\q2 hraba hoi vaiphu dawk ka tahung teh,
\q2 pan ka kângai toe telah a ti.
\p 
\v 7 BAWIPA ni Job koevah lawk be a dei hnukkhu, BAWIPA ni Teman tami Eliphaz koevah, nang hoi na hui roi koevah ka lungkhueknae a kâan. Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka san Job patetlah kaie kong dawk, lawkkatang hah na dei awh hoeh.
\v 8 Hatdawkvah, maitotan 7, tutan 7 hrawi nateh, ka san Job koevah cet awh nateh, nangmouh hanelah thuengnae hah poe awh. Hahoi ka san Job ni nangmouh hanelah a ratoum vaiteh, hote kai ni ka coe pouh han. Nahoeh pawiteh, na pathu awh e patetlah na lathueng lawk na ceng awh han. Bangkongtetpawiteh, ka san Job patetlah kaie kong dawkvah, lawkkatang na dei awh hoeh telah a ti.
\v 9 Hottelah Teman tami Eliphaz hoi Shuhi tami Bildad hoi Naamath tami Zophar tinaw a cei awh teh, BAWIPA ni kâ a poe e patetlah a sak awh teh, BAWIPA ni Job kâheinae hah a coe pouh.
\p 
\v 10 Hahoi Job ni a huinaw kathum touh hanelah, a ratoum pouh torei teh, BAWIPA ni Job kangduenae hmuen hah bout ahawi sak teh, BAWIPA ni Job teh yampa e a tawnta e hlakvah, let hni touh bout a poe.
\v 11 Hottelah a hmaunawnghanaw hoi a tawncanunaw pueng teh, yampa kapanueknaw pueng ni a im dawk a tho awh teh, rawca a ca awh. BAWIPA ni a lathueng vah kathoute a phasak e naw pueng dawk a lungpahawi awh teh a lungmawng sak awh. Tami pueng ni ahni koevah, ngun hoi suinaw hah a poe awh.
\p 
\v 12 Hottelah BAWIPA ni ahmaloe e hlak a hnukteng yawhawinae kapap poung lah a poe. Tu 14,000, kalauk 6,000, maitotan a bo lah 1,000, hoi la manu 1,000 a tawn.
\v 13 Ca tongpa 7 touh hoi canu 3 touh hai a tawn.
\v 14 Apasuekpoung e min teh Jemimah, apâhni e teh Keziah, apâthum e teh Kerenhappukh.
\v 15 Ram thung pueng dawk Job e canu patetlah meikahawi e awm hoeh. A na pa ni ahnimouh teh a thangroinaw koe râw a rei van.
\v 16 Hathnukkhu hoi Job teh kum 140 a hring teh a ca capanaw hoi a na mincanaw se pali totouh a hmu rah.
\v 17 Hottelah Job a matawng teh hnintha kuep lahoi a due. 
